20height%3D%5C%221386%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUniversity%20of%20Pennsylvania%20campus.%3Cp%3EJon%20Lovette%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Education%20Department%20has%20started%20sending%20students'%20FAFSA%20forms%20to%20colleges.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20process%20is%20months%20later%20than%20usual%20this%20year%2C%20leaving%20students%20and%20colleges%20with%20limited%20time%20to%20evaluate%20financial%20aid%20packages.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThere's%20already%20been%20a%20decline%20in%20forms%20submitted%20compared%20to%20last%20year.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20no%20secret%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-repayment-issues-debt-relief-broken-industry-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecollege%20is%20expensive%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20and%20parents%20need%20time%20to%20figure%20out%20how%20they'll%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-value-of-college-higher-education-student-debt-tuition-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eafford%20a%20higher%20education%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20their%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20time%20is%20a%20luxury%20that%20many%20families%20won't%20have.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20because%20the%20Education%20Department%20just%20started%20sending%20students'%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-get-more-financial-aid-student-loans-fafsa-update-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFree%20Application%20for%20Federal%20Student%20Aid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20FAFSA%20forms%20to%20schools%20in%20early%20March%2C%20about%20two%20months%20after%20it%20previously%20planned%20to%20send%20over%20that%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20delay%20is%20due%20to%20changes%20the%20Education%20Department%20enacted%20this%20year%20that%20aimed%20to%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Emake%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-fafsa-form-reddit-parent-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFAFSA%20a%20lot%20easier%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20families%20to%20access.%20The%20idea%20was%20that%20the%20new%20form%20would%20open%20up%20billions%20more%20dollars%20in%20financial%20aid%20for%20families%20by%20implementing%20a%20new%20formula%2C%20along%20with%20streamlining%20the%20number%20of%20questions%20on%20the%20form%20to%20make%20the%20process%20less%20burdensome.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Better%20FAFSA%20makes%20it%20as%20simple%20and%20easy%20as%20possible%20for%20families%20to%20get%20help%20paying%20for%20college%2C%20and%20updating%20our%20tables%20will%20help%20even%20more%20students%20get%20the%20help%20they%20need%2C%26quot%3B%20Under%20Secretary%20of%20Education%20James%20Kvaal%20previously%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20%26quot%3BUpdating%20our%20calculations%20will%20help%20students%20qualify%20for%20as%20much%20financial%20aid%20as%20possible.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffafsa-why-parents-students-have-to-wait-financial-aid-awards-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethose%20updates%20came%20with%20delays%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20Education%20Department%20pushed%20back%20the%20timeline%20to%20start%20sending%20students'%20FAFSA%20forms%20to%20schools%2C%20which%20resulted%20in%20fewer%20students%20submitting%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethem%20at%20all.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncan.org%2Fpage%2FFAFSAtracker%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAccording%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20National%20College%20Attainment%20Network%2C%20which%20helps%20students%20prepare%20for%20college%2C%20through%20March%208%2C%20just%20over%2030%25%20of%20high%20school%20seniors%20submitted%20their%20applications%2C%20which%20is%20down%20by%20nearly%2033%25%20compared%20to%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20applications%20could%20tick%20up%20in%20the%20coming%20weeks%2C%20the%20lower%20numbers%20will%20leave%20colleges%20with%20limited%20time%20to%20evaluate%20students'%20applications%20and%20get%20them%20their%20reward%20letters%20in%20time%20for%20the%20commitment%20deadlines%20in%20May.%20On%20top%20of%20that%2C%20fewer%20applications%20could%20mean%20lower%20enrollment%20for%20freshmen%20in%20the%20fall%20%E2%80%94%20another%20bad%20sign%20for%20colleges%20caused%20by%20the%20FAFSA%20delays.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJustin%20Drager%2C%20president%20and%20CEO%20of%20the%20National%20Association%20of%20Student%20Financial%20Aid%20Administrators%2C%20and%20Ted%20Mitchell%2C%20president%20of%20the%20American%20Council%20on%20Education%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2024%2F02%2F08%2Fopinion%2Ffafsa-delay-college-access.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrote%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20February%20opinion%20piece%20in%20The%20New%20York%20Times%20that%20the%20FAFSA%20delays%20%26quot%3Bthreaten%20to%20harm%20the%20very%20students%20and%20families%20that%20financial%20aid%20is%20intended%20to%20help.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20students%20may%20be%20pressured%20into%20making%20one%20of%20the%20most%20significant%20financial%20decisions%20of%20their%20lives%20without%20having%20a%20complete%20picture%20of%20their%20options%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BOthers%20may%20delay%20enrolling%20in%20college%20for%20another%20year%2C%20once%20the%20aid%20application%20process%20is%20running%20more%20smoothly.%20Or%2C%20worse%20yet%2C%20some%20students%20may%20become%20so%20frustrated%20by%20the%20complexity%20and%20confusion%20of%20this%20year's%20financial%20aid%20process%20that%20they%20give%20up%20altogether.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20the%20delays%2C%20some%20colleges%20have%20been%20pushing%20back%20their%20commitment%20deadlines%20to%20give%20families%20more%20time%20to%20account%20for%20their%20financial%20aid%20rewards.%20For%20example%2C%20the%20University%20of%20Pennsylvania's%20State%20System%20of%20Higher%20Education%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.passhe.edu%2Fnews%2Freleases%2F2024-02-19_new-student-commitment-extension.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eannounced%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20February%20that%20the%2010%20universities%20in%20the%20system%20would%20be%20extending%20their%20commitment%20deadline%20to%20at%20least%20May%2015%20instead%20of%20holding%20students%20to%20the%20typical%20May%201%20deadline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20know%20that%20most%20of%20our%20students%20are%20from%20low-%20and%20middle-income%20families%2C%20and%20they%20rely%20on%20financial%20aid%20to%20attend%20their%20PASSHE%20university%2C%26quot%3B%20PASSHE%20Chancellor%20Dan%20Greenstein%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20%26quot%3BGoing%20to%20college%20and%20earning%20a%20degree%20or%20credential%20is%20life%20changing%2C%20and%20those%20decisions%20should%20not%20be%20rushed.%20This%20extension%20gives%20students%20the%20time%20and%20flexibility%20to%20consider%20their%20financial%20aid%20options%20and%20make%20informed%20decisions.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKvaal%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-get-more-financial-aid-student-loans-fafsa-update-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epreviously%20told%3C%2Fa%3E%20Business%20Insider%20that%20he's%20glad%20schools%20are%20being%20flexible%20with%20their%20commitment%20deadlines%20to%20give%20students%20more%20time%20to%20make%20decisions%2C%20and%20he%20encouraged%20schools%20who%20have%20not%20done%20so%20yet%20to%20take%20their%20deadlines%20into%20account%2C%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20meantime%2C%20Republican%20lawmakers%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.help.senate.gov%2Franking%2Fnewsroom%2Fpress%2Franking-member-cassidy-chairwoman-foxx-colleagues-request-investigation-into-biden-admins-botched-fafsa-rollout-impact-on-students-and-schools%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Easked%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20Government%20Accountability%20Office%20to%20investigate%20the%20Education%20Department's%20FAFSA%20rollout%2C%20writing%20in%20their%20letter%20that%20%26quot%3Ball%20these%20challenges%20and%20delays%20may%20cause%20some%20students%E2%80%94particularly%20low-income%20students%20who%20are%20most%20dependent%20on%20federal%20aid%E2%80%94to%20give%20up%20and%20not%20pursue%20postsecondary%20education.%26quot%3B%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAre%20you%20a%20student%20or%20parent%20struggling%20to%20navigate%20the%20FAFSA%20process%3F%20Share%20your%20story%20with%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aasheffey%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Easheffey%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffafsa-how-to-get-college-financial-aid-chaotic-rollout-delays-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711099561000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65fc72a8895d822030330d87%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffafsa-how-to-get-college-financial-aid-chaotic-rollout-delays-2024-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20chaotic%20FAFSA%20rollout%20means%20financial%20aid%20reward%20letters%20will%20be%20delayed%20for%20many%2C%20limiting%20the%20time%20they%20have%20to%20craft%20their%20college%20budgets.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22asheffey%40businessinsider.com%20(Ayelet%20Sheffey)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffafsa-how-to-get-college-financial-aid-chaotic-rollout-delays-2024-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Russian%20missile%20strikes%20cause%20Ukraine%20power%20cuts%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711099275000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F1724E%2Fproduction%