20his%20favorite%20for%20one%20big%20reason%3A%20it's%20got%20everything.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20has%20beaches%2C%20it%20has%20mountains%2C%20it%20has%20deserts%2C%20it%20has%20islands%2C%20it%20has%20great%20cities%2C%20it%20has%20good%20cities%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BNo%20matter%20what%20you%20like%20%E2%80%94%20I%20don't%20care%20who%20you%20are%20%E2%80%94%20there%20is%20something%20for%20you%20here.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbbamonte%20is%20partial%20to%20California%20because%20it%20has%20nine%20national%20parks%2C%20the%20most%20of%20any%20state%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20he%20said%20the%20only%20time%20he's%20felt%20a%20bit%20unsafe%20in%20the%20US%20was%20in%20San%20Francisco%2C%20Abbamonte%20said%20he's%20been%20back%20several%20times%20and%20still%20thinks%20it's%20a%20%26quot%3Bpretty%20great%20city.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThere%20is%20more%20to%20Colorado%20than%20good%20skiing.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22There%20is%20more%20to%20Colorado%20than%20skiing.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65fb0284895d822030329386%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22719%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThere%20is%20more%20to%20Colorado%20than%20skiing.%3Cp%3EKruck20%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EColorado%20is%20second%20on%20Abbamonte's%20list%2C%20mainly%20because%20of%20how%20versatile%20the%20topography%20is%20and%20how%20%26quot%3Bgreat%26quot%3B%20the%20national%20parks%20are.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BColorado%20is%20just%20all%20about%20the%20mountains.%20I'm%20not%20even%20a%20skier%2C%20but%20I%20like%20going%20to%20ski%20towns%20and%20doing%20everything%20else%20but%20skiing.%20I%20also%20like%20going%20to%20ski%20towns%20in%20the%20summer%20because%20I%20love%20hiking%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BEastern%20Colorado%20is%20just%20like%20this%20whole%20other%20oasis%20of%20plains.%26quot%3B%3C%2F