C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20is%20a%20fan%20of%20Honolulu%2C%20which%20he%20said%20is%20incredibly%20%26quot%3Bunderrated.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20the%20big%20volcano%20and%20Waikiki%20Beach%2C%20which%20is%20a%20beautiful%20beach%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20reason%20Obama%20still%20goes%20back%20there%20on%20vacations.%20It's%20absolutely%20awesome.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ENevada%20is%20a%20dream%2C%20no%20matter%20the%20season.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lake%20Tahoe%20is%20the%20most%20beautiful%20thing%20in%20the%20US.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65fb05a34af076d3cf91fd67%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22853%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELake%20Tahoe%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20beautiful%20sights%20in%20the%20US.%3Cp%3EMariuszBlach%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ENevada%20combines%20the%20best%20of%20Arizona%20and%20Utah%20because%20it%20has%20both%20natural%20beauty%20and%20a%20lot%20of%20desert%20vistas%2C%20Abbamonte%20said.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20he%20likes%20Las%20Vegas%2C%20he%20added%2C%20Lake%20Tahoe%20is%20the%20main%20reason%20Nevada%20makes%20his%20top%20six%20states%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20probably%20the%20most%20beautiful%20thing%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI've%20been%20there%20in%20the%20summer%20and%20the%20winter%20a%20dozen%20times%2C%20and%20it's%20like%20a%20dream.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Abbamonte%20ranked%20Louisiana%2047th%20out%20of%2050%20states.%20It%20would've%20been%20farther%20down%20if%20it%20wasn't%20for%20New%20Orleans.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22New%20Orleans%20elevates%20Louisiana.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65fb0a094af076d3cf92000e%3Fformat%3Djp