%20of%20the%20internship%2C%20everyone%20met%20with%20HR%20and%20was%20either%20presented%20with%20an%20offer%20letter%20or%20told%20they%20weren't%20offered%20a%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EStart%20building%20your%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20years%20in%20advance%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EStart%20as%20early%20as%20possible%20to%20build%20experience%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-write-the-perfect-resume-2012-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eparticipate%20in%20extracurriculars%3C%2Fa%3E%20relevant%20to%20your%20desired%20position%2C%20and%20show%20your%20passions.%20I%20fundraised%20for%20breast%20cancer%20research%2C%20was%20a%20teaching%20assistant%20for%20a%20marketing%20and%20business%20analysis%20course%2C%20and%20was%20a%20peer%20mentor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExtracurriculars%20should%20be%20something%20you're%20genuinely%20interested%20in%20and%20should%20show%20a%20story%20over%20multiple%20years.%20They're%20discussed%20in%20the%20interview%2C%20and%20a%20candidate's%20passion%20for%20these%20activities%20comes%20through%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20with%20follow-up%20questions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EResearch%20the%20job%20position%20and%20the%20different%20groups%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EResearching%20the%20company%20is%20essential%20for%20positions%20right%20out%20of%20college.%20For%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquit-dream-job-jpmorgan-banking-not-for-me-singapore-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJPMorgan's%3C%2Fa%3E%20internship%20and%20analyst%20programs%2C%20you're%20usually%20placed%20in%20a%20large%20group%20with%20many%20different%20focus%20areas.%20You%20can%20have%20a%20particular%20interest%20in%20one%2C%20but%20be%20knowledgeable%20about%20all%20of%20them.%20%3Cspan%3EI%20was%20drawn%20to%20prime%20brokerage%20because%20it's%20fast-paced%20and%20I%20wanted%20to%20be%20in%20a%20client-facing%20role.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20inter