%20AAP%3F%20Seven%20Questions%20After%20Kejriwal's%20Arrest%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-01%2F5hv1ac4o_arvindkejriwal_625x300_30_January_20.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcan-arvind-kejriwal-govern-delhi-after-arrest-what-jail-rules-say-5288034%5C%22%3EAam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20been%20claiming%20for%20quite%20some%20time%20that%20its%20leader%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexplained-why-enforcement-directorate-wants-to-arrest-arvind-kejriwal-5284508%5C%22%3EArvind%20Kejrwal%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20would%20be%20arrested.%20The%20day%20finally%20came%20on%20March%2021%2C%20when%20in%20a%20late-night%20move%2C%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwal-arrested-by-enforcement-directorate-in-liquor-policy-case-5284679%5C%22%3Earrested%20Kejriwal%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20his%20alleged%20involvement%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwal-spends-night-at-probe-agency-office-after-arrest-5287764%5C%22%3EDelhi%20liquor%20scam%3C%2Fa%3E.%20After%20Jharkhand's%20Hemant%20Soren%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhemant-sorens-judicial-custody-extended-till-april-4-in-land-scam-case-5284672%5C%22%3EKejriwal%20is%20now%20possibly%20the%20first%20chief%20minister%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20have%20been%20arrested%20while%20in%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncidentally%2C%20for%20both%20leaders%2C%20skipping%20the%20ninth%20summons%20by%20the%20central%20agency%20proved%20to%20be%20dangerous.%20Upon%20Kejriwal's%20arrest%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwal-withdraws-petition-against-arrest-from-supreme-court-5288477%5C%22%3EAAP%20moved%20the%20Supreme%20Court%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20a%20late-night%20hearing%2C%20which%20was%20rejected.%20The%20party%20later%20withdrew%20its%20petition%20and%20will%20now%20approach%20a%20trial%20court.%20However%2C%20under%20the%20stringent%20rules%20of%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%20(PMLA)%2C%202002%2C%20getting%20relief%20from%20courts%20is%20not%20easy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Big%20Blow%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20development%20is%20a%20big%20blow%20to%20AAP.%20Delhi's%20former%20deputy%20chief%20minister%2C%20Manish%20Sisodia%2C%20is%20already%20in%20jail%20in%20connection%20with%20a%20corruption%20case.%20It's%20ironic%20that%20a%20party%20formed%20out%20of%20a%20movement%20against%20corruption%20is%20today%20facing%20arrest%20of%20its%20top%20leadership%20in%20corruption%20cases.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20has%20many%20angles%20-%20legal%2C%20political%20and%20ethical%2C%20moral.%20While%20the%20AAP%20has%20accused%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20of%20using%20central%20agencies%20to%20finish%20off%20the%20party%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20countered%20that%20charge%20by%20claiming%20that%20the%20law%20is%20taking%20its%20due%20course%20and%20the%20party%20is%20paying%20for%20its%20illegal%20deeds%20in%20the%20liquor%20case.%20The%20AAP%20questions%20the%20timing%20of%20the%20arrest%2C%20alleging%20that%20the%20move%20is%20aimed%20at%20preventing%20Kejriwal%20from%20campaigning%20for%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20but%20the%20BJP%20says%20that%20it%20is%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20Kejriwal%20who%20timed%20his%20actions%20well%20to%20gain%20sympathy%20from%20voters.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20seven%20unanswered%20questions%20that%20emanate%20from%20this%20arrest.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Who%20Will%20Be%20The%20Next%20CM%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20AAP%20has%20claimed%20that%20Kejriwal%20will%20continue%20to%20be%20chief%20minister%20and%20run%20the%20government%20from%20jail%2C%20is%20it%20legally%20tenable%3F%20He%20is%20a%20chief%20minister%20without%20any%20portfolio.%20As%20he%20has%20not%20yet%20been%20convicted%2C%20Kejriwal%20cannot%20be%20disqualified%20as%20an%20MLA.%20And%20this%20means%20that%20he%20is%20eligible%20to%20be%20chief%20minister%2C%20too.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20this%20may%20sound%20fine%20in%20theory%2C%20does%20the%20spirit%20of%20law%20allow%20this%3F%20Will%20it%20be%20morally%2Fethically%20right%20to%20continue%20as%20chief%20minister%3F%20Can%20the%20Lieutenant-Governor%20(L-G)%2C%20with%20whom%20the%20AAP%20doesn't%20enjoy%20a%20good%20rapport%2C%20intervene%20and%20remove%20Kejriwal%20as%20chief%20minister%20or%20take%20the%20reins%20of%20the%20government%3F%20This%20remains%20to%20be%20seen.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Will%20The%20Arrest%20Create%20Sympathy%20For%20AAP%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20million-dollar%20question.%20The%20saga%20clearly%20consolidates%20the%20AAP's%20support%20amongst%20its%20core%20voters.%20However%2C%20outside%20of%20Delhi%20and%20Punjab%2C%20this%20factor%20may%20not%20resonate%20with%20the%20electorate%20as%20much.%20Since%20the%20AAP%20has%20national%20ambitions%2C%20the%20arrest%20may%20hinder%20the%20party's%20expansion%20plans%20as%20the%20ED%20action%20severely%20dents%20its%20%26quot%3Bparty%20with%20a%20difference%26quot%3B%20image.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Will%20This%20Sympathy%20Work%20In%20State%20Or%20National%20Polls%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20as%20a%20state%20sees%20split%20voting%2C%20that%20is%2C%20a%20large%20number%20of%20voters%20back%20AAP%20in%20state%20elections%20but%20vote%20for%20the%20BJP%20in%20national%20elections.%20This%20means%20that%20there%20is%20a%20good%20number%20of%20swing%20or%20neutral%20voters%20in%20the%20capital.%20How%20will%20Kejriwal's%20arrest%20impact%20this%20segment%3F%20Even%20if%20a%20section%20of%20voters%20feels%20that%20Kejriwal%20is%20being%20targeted%20by%20the%20BJP%20through%20central%20agencies%2C%20will%20this%20work%20to%20his%20advantage%20in%20state%20elections%20due%20early%20next%20year%2C%20or%20even%20the%20general%20elections%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi's%20poll%20date%2C%20May%2025%2C%20is%20still%20a%20good%20two%20months%20away.%20Has%20the%20BJP%20unknowingly%20presented%20the%20state%20on%20a%20platter%20to%20AAP%3F%20In%202025%2C%20the%20party%20completes%20a%20decade%20in%20office.%20Can%20it%20neutralise%20anti-incumbency%20against%20the%20Kejriwal%20government%20in%20the%202025%20assembly%20elections%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20Can%20The%20Arrest%20Unite%20The%20Opposition%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20key%20allies%20exiting%20before%20polls%20and%20seat-sharing%20pacts%20not%20yet%20finalised%20for%20key%20states%20like%20Maharashtra%20and%20Bihar%2C%20the%20Opposition%20had%20been%20in%20disarray.%20But%20today%2C%20the%20Congress%2C%20whose%20Delhi%20leaders%20were%20ironically%20the%20ones%20who%20had%20exposed%20the%20alleged%20liquor%20scam%2C%20is%20now%20firmly%20backing%20the%20AAP%20on%20this%20issue.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20top%20guns%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20have%20come%20out%20in%20support%20of%20Kejriwal.%20This%20arrest%20has%20ended%20up%20seving%20as%20a%20unifier%20for%20the%20Opposition%20alliance%20and%20has%20given%20it%20a%20set%20of%20muddas-that%20the%20BJP%20is%20out%20to%20kill%20competition%2C%20that%20there%20is%20no%20level%20playing%20field%20in%20the%20elections%2C%20and%20that%20democracy%20is%20in%20danger.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20Can%20It%20Backfire%20Against%20The%20BJP%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20is%20clearly%20in%20the%20pole%20position%20in%20general%20elections%20according%20to%20opinion%20polls.%20Often%2C%20when%20a%20party%20is%20in%20power%2C%20it%20tends%20to%20get%20overconfident%20and%20ignore%20the%20warning%20signals.%20Such%20actions%20can%20spur%20the%20opposition%20and%20give%20it%20ammunition.%20This%20could%20have%20an%20impact%20on%20voters%20who%20want%20India%20to%20have%20a%20shashakt%20opposition.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E6.%20Who%20Will%20Lead%20AAP's%20Lok%20Sabha%20Campaign%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP%20is%20very%20much%20dependent%20on%20Kejriwal%20as%20he%20is%20their%20star%20campaigner.%20Over%20the%20years%2C%20many%20founding%20members%20of%20the%20party%20have%20left%20due%20to%20differences%20with%20Kejriwal%2C%20accusing%20him%20of%20being%20stubborn%20and%20autocratic.%20With%20Sisodia%20also%20behind%20bars%2C%20the%20party%20does%20not%20have%20many%20leaders%20with%20a%20pan-India%20appeal.%20To%20an%20extent%2C%20the%20burden%20may%20fall%20upon%20Punjab%20Chief%20Minister%20Bhagwant%20Mann.%20In%20Delhi%2C%20Atishi%20and%20Saurav%20Bhardwaj%20may%20hold%20the%20fort.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E7.%20Is%20It%20The%20End%20Of%20The%20Road%20For%20AAP%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP%20was%20born%20from%20a%20public%20movement%20against%20corruption.%20In%20just%20a%20decade%2C%20it%20has%20acquired%20a%20national%20party%20status.%20It%20is%20the%20only%20party%20apart%20from%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20BJP%20to%20have%20a%20government%20in%20more%20than%20one%20state.%20It%20has%20also%20expanded%20its%20presence%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20Goa%20and%20Haryana%2C%20and%20is%20considered%20by%20many%20as%20having%20the%20potential%20to%20take%20over%20the%20mantle%20from%20the%20Congress%20as%20the%20main%20opposition%20party.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20will%20have%20to%20see%20how%20things%20pan%20out%20legally%20and%20politically%20in%20the%20next%20few%20days%20to%20gauge%20exactly%20how%20Kejriwal's%