he%20Gun%3C%2Fi%3E%2C%20Bhutan%E2%80%99s%20official%20entry%20to%20the%20Oscars%20directed%20by%20Pawo%20Choyning%20Dorji%20%E2%80%94%20the%20records%20from%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Information%20and%20Broadcasting%20revealed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20film%20festivals%2C%20the%20government%20waives%20the%20requirement%20for%20a%20certificate%20from%20the%20Central%20Board%20of%20Film%20Certification%20(CBFC).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmib.gov.in%2Fcodesguidelinespolicies%2Fpolicy-certification-films-film-festivals%5C%22%3Epolicy%20for%20certification%20of%20films%20for%20film%20festivals%3C%2Fa%3E%20notified%20in%20January%202006%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20order%20to%20consider%20the%20request%20for%20exemption%20from%20the%20process%20of%20certification%20for%20films%20to%20be%20screened%20in%20festivals%2C%20the%20following%20documents%20shall%20be%20sent%20by%20the%20Director%20of%20the%20Festival%20addressed%20to%20Joint%20Secretary%20(Films)%20along%20with%20the%20request%20for%20exemption%3A%20(i)%20List%20of%20films%20to%20be%20screened%20in%20the%20festival%2C%20(ii)%20Synopsis%20of%20each%20of%20the%20films%2C%20(iii)%20Composition%20of%20the%20Preview%20Committee%2C%20which%20should%20comprise%20persons%20who%20are%20related%20to%20the%20film%20industry%20or%20are%20critics%2Fwriters%20connected%20with%20film%2C%20(iv)%20Report%20of%20the%20Preview%20Committee%20certifying%20that%20the%20films%20have%20been%20recommended%20for%20exhibition%20at%20the%20festival%2C%20(v)%20Certificate%20from%20the%20Director%20of%20the%20Festival%20to%20the%20effect%20that%20the%20screening%20of%20such%20films%20would%20be%20limited%20to%20delegates%20(definition%20of%20delegates%20would%20include%20film-makers%2C%20media%20students%2C%20critics%2C%20film%20theorists%2C%20film%20lovers%20and%20all%20those%20associated%20with%20the%20production%20and%20business%20of%20film%20and%20members%20of%20the%20press%20duly%20registered%20with%20the%20festival%20authorities%20as%20well%20as%20its%20jury)%2C%20(vi)%20Certificate%20from%20the%20Director%20of%20the%20Festival%20to%20the%20effect%20that%20the%20festival%20is%20non-commercial%20in%20nature.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%C2%A0%3Ci%3EThe%20Monk%20and%20the%20Gun%2C%20%3C%2Fi%3Ea%20satire%20featuring%20mock%20elections%20in%20Bhutan%C2%A0was%20screened%20in%20the%20Bengaluru%20International%20film%20festival%20(BIFFes)%20held%20from%20February%2029%E2%80%93March%207%2C%202024.%20The%20film%20was%20also%20shown%20at%20the%20Jio%20Mumbai%20Academy%20of%20Moving%20Image%20(MAMI)%20Film%20Festival%20held%20from%20October%2027%2C%20November%205%2C%202023%2C%20in%20which%20it%20won%20the%20Audience%20Choice%20Award.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Dorji%E2%80%99s%20film%20is%20set%20to%20be%20released%20theatrically%20in%20India%20and%20the%20trailer%20of%20the%20film%20is%20being%20shown%20in%20cinemas%20across%20the%20country%20after%20the%20CBFC%20granted%20permission%20for%20the%20same.%20Hence%2C%20it%20is%20unclear%20why%20the%20the%20ministry%20denied%20permission%20for%20its%20screening%20in%20IFFI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711093523000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F22125935%2FScreenshot-2024-03-22-at-12.58.23-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmovies%2Funion-government-denied-screening-of-4-films-in-international-film-festival-of-india-in-2023%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20films%20which%20were%20denied%20permission%20were%20set%20In%20Bhutan%2C%20Gaza%2C%20Turkey%20and%20Hungary.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmovies%2Funion-government-denied-screening-of-4-films-in-international-film-festival-of-india-in-2023%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Minors%20Beaten%2C%20Blatant%20Casteism%3A%20What%20Followed%20a%20Case%20of%20Theft%20in%20Mumbai%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F02%2F11082632%2FImage6.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EMumbai%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20It%20was%20a%20case%20of%20roadside%20theft.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETwenty-three-year-old%20Samina%20Shaikh%20was%20out%20shopping%20for%20Eid%20when%20she%20realised%20her%20purse%20had%20been%20slit%20and%20cash%20amounting%20to%20Rs%2064%2C000%20that%20she%20had%20withdrawn%20from%20a%20nearby%20bank%20had%20been%20stolen.%20Shaikh%20did%20not%20notice%20if%20it%20was%20one%20person%20or%20more%20but%20could%20recall%20the%20presence%20of%20several%20young%20children%20in%20the%20crowded%20market%20road%20of%20the%20Shivaji%20Nagar%20slums%20that%20evening.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20could%20be%2016%20or%2014%20or%20even%2011%2C%20it%20is%20difficult%20to%20tell.%20They%20were%20all%20so%20young%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%20The%20theft%20took%20place%20on%20March%207%20and%20Shaikh%C2%A0%20approached%20the%20Shivaji%20Nagar%20police%20station%20on%20the%20same%20evening.%20The%20police%2C%20however%2C%20did%20not%20budge%20until%20local%20leaders%20intervened.%20The%20FIR%20was%20lodged%20only%20on%20March%209.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20could%20have%20been%20a%20case%20of%20theft%20not%20unlike%20the%20many%20registered%20every%20day%20across%20the%20country%20then%20led%20to%20a%20series%20of%20events%20exposing%20police%20brutality%2C%20blatant%20casteism%2C%20and%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20apathy%20towards%20children%20belonging%20to%20marginalised%20identities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20police%20initially%20rounded%20up%20eight%20children%2C%20all%20between%2011%20and%2015%20years%20of%20age.%20Three%20of%20them%20belonged%20to%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.roundtableindia.co.in%2Fsociological-understanding-of-wadar-community-in-an-urban-region%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EWadar%20community%20and%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0the%20rest%20were%20from%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsociety%2Fdecades-after-denotification-pardhis-in-maharashtra-struggle-to-stave-off-criminal-tag%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EPardhi%20tribe%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Both%20communities%20are%20highly%20criminalised%20and%20exploited%2C%20and%20largely%20lead%20migratory%20lives%20without%20proper%20shelter%20and%20citizens%E2%80%99%20rights.%20Most%20of%20those%20detained%20were%20girls.%20One%2020-year-old%20woman%20was%20rounded%20up%20too.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShaikh%2C%20although%20not%20entirely%20sure%2C%20said%20one%20boy%E2%80%99s%20face%20looked%20%E2%80%9Cfamiliar%E2%80%9D%20to%20her.%20He%20was%20the%20oldest%2C%20around%2016.%20The%20police%20roughed%20up%20the%20boy%20and%20his%20friend%2C%20who%20was%20even%20younger.%20One%20of%20them%20even%20confessed%20to%20their%20mistake%20but%20they%20were%20soon%20released.%20Their%20parents%20came%20by%20and%20were%20made%20to%20pay%20an%20amount%20to%20the%20cops.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20other%20kids%20%E2%80%93%20all%20from%20Mumbai%E2%80%99s%20most%20impoverished%20M%20East%20ward%2C%20located%20on%20the%20northern%20edge%20of%20the%20metropolis%20%E2%80%93%20were%20kept%20in%20the%20police%20station%20and%20say%20they%20were%20brutalised.%20Bringing%20young%20children%20to%20a%20police%20station%2C%20even%20when%20they%20are%20in%20conflict%20with%20the%20law%2C%20is%20prohibited.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Took%20turns%20to%20beat%20me%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%2020-year-old%20woman%20who%20was%20held%20by%20police%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20each%20one%20of%20them%20were%20beaten%20on%20their%20palms%20and%20feet%20with%20a%20belt%20and%20bamboo%20stick.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20wanted%20us%20to%20accept%20a%20crime%20that%20none%20of%20us%20were%20involved%20in%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHer%2011-year-old%20brother%20appeared%20to%20have%20been%20the%20worst%20affected.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20hands%20and%20legs%20were%20tied%20up%20and%20they%20took%20turns%20to%20beat%20me%20up%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20boy%2C%20who%20is%20visibly%20frail%2C%20shared.%20One%20of%20the%20younger%20girls%2C%20around%2013%20years%20old%2C%20who%20had%20a%20few%20coins%20hidden%20in%20her%20inners%2C%20was%20made%20to%20open%20them%20and%20show%20the%20coins%20to%20the%20gathered%20policemen.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Police%20also%20hurled%20casteist%20slurs%20at%20the%20children%20%E2%80%93%20it%20must%20be%20stressed%20that%20they%20all%20belonged%20to%20the%20highly%20criminalised%20Pardhi%20tribe.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20constable%20kept%20calling%20us%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ethieves%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20kept%20invoking%20our%20caste%20while%20beating%20us.%20He%20said%20Pardhis%20are%20all%20thieves%2C%E2%80%9D%20one%20of%20the%20younger%20children%20said.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20police%20let%20off%20all%20the%20girls%20at%20around%20midnight%2C%20the%20young%20boy%20was%20detained%20at%20the%20police%20station%20for%20close%20to%2024%20hours.%20He%20said%20he%20was%20hungry%20and%20sore%20from%20all%20the%20beatings.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%2020-year-old%20had%20been%20detained%20when%20she%20was%20carrying%20her%20three-year-old%20niece.%20She%20said%20that%20as%20the%20baby%E2%80%99s%20aunt%2C%20two%20siblings%20and%20cousins%20were%20beaten%20up%2C%20the%20baby%20sat%20unattended%20without%20food%20or%20water%20for%20close%20to%20eight%20hours.%20Later%20at%20midnight%2C%20the%20police%20allowed%20the%20girls%20to%20leave.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20walked%20over%202%20kilometres%20at%20around%20midnight%20to%20reach%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%2020-year-old%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20boy%20could%20finally%20be%20rescued%20only%20after%20the%20girls%20reached%20home%20and%20alerted%20a%20local%20social%20worker%2C%20Shubham%20Kothari%2C%20about%20the%20police%E2%80%99s%20excesses.%20Kothari%20mobilised%20his%20network%20and%20information%20soon%20reached%20the%20Child%20Welfare%20Committee%E2%80%99s%20suburban%20division%20and%20CHILDLINE%20India%20Foundation%20(CIF)%2C%20a%20nodal%20agency%20of%20the%20Union%20Ministry%20of%20Women%20and%20Child%20Development%2C%20involved%20in%20rescuing%20children%20in%20unsafe%20conditions.%20Child%20Safety%20Forum%2C%20a%20collective%20of%20NGOs%2C%20jumped%20in%20too.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERescuers%20arrive%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENeha%20Pednekar%2C%20a%20seasoned%20supervisor%20at%20the%20CHILDLINE%20says%20when%20she%20reached%20the%20police%20station%2C%20she%20found%20the%2011-year-old%20boy%20on%20the%20third%20floor%20of%20the%20police%20station%2C%20terrified%20and%20hungry.%20%E2%80%9CHis%20feet%20were%20swollen%20and%20he%20was%20unable%20to%20walk%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%20Pednekar%20took%20charge%20of%20the%20situation%20and%20rescued%20the%20child.%20She%2C%20along%20with%20the%20boy%20and%20the%20five%20other%20girls%20headed%20to%20the%20municipal%20corporation-run%20Shatabdi%20Hospital%20close%20by%2C%20even%20as%20the%20police%20persuaded%20her%20to%20not%20%E2%80%9Cescalate%20the%20matter%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20the%20police%20brutality%20towards%20such%20young%20children%20had%20already%20shocked%20me%2C%20I%20was%20further%20appalled%20by%20the%20police%E2%80%99s%20attitude.%20The%20police%20truly%20believed%20they%20had%20done%20no%20wrong%20and%20illegally%20detaining%20children%20and%20brutalising%20them%20was%20the%20only%20way%20to%20solve%20a%20crime%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pednekar%20said.%20Pednekar%20and%20other%20rights%20activists%20have%20ever%20since%20been%20demanding%20an%20FIR%20be%20registered%20against%20the%20four%20policemen%20and%20a%20lady%20constable%20who%20had%20brutalised%20the%20children.%20While%20this%20FIR%20has%20not%20been%20registered%20at%20all%2C%20an%20FIR%2C%20naming%20these%20children%2C%20was%20registered%20as%20soon%20as%20CHILDLINE%20and%20CWC%20intervened.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20medical%20report%2C%20accessed%20by%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20confirms%20the%20violence.%20The%20forensic%20report%20says%20they%20were%20beaten%20up%20with%20a%20%E2%80%9Cblunt%20object%E2%80%9D.%20The%20reports%20by%20the%20Probation%20Officer%20and%20District%20Child%20Protection%20Officer%20also%20state%20that%20the%20children%20were%20physically%20assaulted%2C%20verbally%20assaulted%20and%20denied%20food%20and%20water.%20The%20children%2C%20who%20after%20being%20rescued%20from%20the%20police%20station%2C%20were%20kept%20at%20a%20children%E2%80%99s%20home%20under%20the%20CWC%E2%80%99s%20care%20to%20protect%20them%20from%20further%20police%20pressure%2C%20finally%20returned%20home%20on%20March%2019.%20The%20police%20tried%20every%20tactic%20in%20the%20book%20to%20squeeze%20out%20favourable%20testimonies%20from%20them.%20The%20CWC%20staff%20said%20that%20they%20had%20to%20push%20back%20in%20at%20least%20two%20occasions%20and%20send%20the%20police%20back.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Coercion%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%2020-year-old%2C%20who%20continued%20to%20live%20in%20the%20slum%2C%20however%2C%20did%20not%20have%20much%20by%20way%20of%20protection.%20The%20same%20men%20who%20had%20brutally%20beaten%20her%20came%20to%20her%20residence%20and%20forced%20her%20to%20sign%20a%20pre-typed%20statement.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20didn%E2%80%99t%20read%20it%20out%20to%20me.%20When%20I%20opposed%2C%20they%20made%20my%20younger%20sister%20(a%20minor)%20sign%20it%20as%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20The%20police%20in%20all%20their%20aggression%2C%20however%2C%20missed%20a%20crucial%20bit.%20The%2020-year-old%20is%20unlettered%20and%20does%20not%20know%20how%20to%20write%20her%20name%20or%20sign.%20She%20uses%20her%20thumb%20impression.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20as%20the%20younger%20kids%20stayed%20in%20the%20CWC%E2%80%99s%20care%20and%20protection%2C%20this%20young%20woman%20continued%20her%20fight%20against%20the%20police.%20Meanwhile%2C%20multiple%20complaints%20were%20made%20to%20the%20Maharashtra%20State%20Child%20Rights%20Commission%20(MSCRC)%20and%20the%20young%20woman%20was%20finally%20summoned%20before%20the%20commission.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20chairperson%20Susieben%20Shah%20had%20also%20summoned%20the%20erring%20policemen%2C%20and%20Deepak%20Pandey%2C%20the%20special%20inspector%20general%20of%20police%20(prevention%20of%20crimes%20against%20women%20and%20children).%20Pandey%2C%20however%2C%20did%20not%20turn%20up%20at%20the%20commission%20as%20a%20respondent%20but%20went%20as%20a%20part%20of%20the%20panel.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F22131137%2FGJHwbI0WAAABGoi-1024x768.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F22131137%2FGJHwbI0WAAABGoi-1024x768.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F22131137%2FGJHwbI0WAAABGoi-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F22131137%2FGJHwbI0WAAABGoi.jpeg%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-702811%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22630%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAn%20image%20of%20the%20hearing%20chaired%20by%20MSCRC%20chairperson%20Susieben%20Shah.%20Deepak%20Pandey%20is%20in%20orange.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40shahsusieben%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20case%20of%20Deepak%20Pandey%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20the%20young%20woman%20reached%20the%20commission%20with%20her%20mother%2C%20she%20was%20taken%20aback%20to%20see%20Pandey%20sit%20alongside%20Shah%20and%20conduct%20the%20hearing.%20Pandey%2C%20from%20the%20very%20onset%20according%20to%20multiple%20accounts%2C%20was%20aggressive%2C%20and%20talked%20down%20anyone%20who%20pointed%20fingers%20at%20the%20errant%20policemen.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20lawyers%20and%20rights%20activists%20asked%20pointed%20questions%20as%20to%20why%20children%20were%20even%20taken%20to%20the%20police%20station%20in%20clear%20violation%20of%20the%20Juvenile%20Justice%20(Care%20and%20Protection%20of%20Children)%20Act%202015%2C%20Pandey%20tried%20to%20deflect%20the%20conversation%20by%20talking%20about%20the%20children%E2%80%99s%20education.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20When%20the%20CWC%20chairperson%20Sunil%20Shirishkar%20objected%20to%20Pandey%E2%80%99s%20tone%20and%20language%2C%20Pandey%20went%20to%20an%20extent%20of%20blaming%20the%20CWC%20for%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20doing%20his%20job%E2%80%9D.%20When%20Pednekar%20told%20the%20commission%20that%20she%20was%20the%20one%20who%20rescued%20the%20young%20boy%20from%20Shivaji%20Nagar%20Police%20station%2C%20Pandey%20screamed%20at%20her%20for%20being%20at%20the%20police%20station%20in%20the%20first%20place.%20Shah%20did%20very%20little%20to%20control%20Pandey.%20The%20young%20woman%20broke%20down%20during%20the%20hearing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShah%20finally%20issued%20an%20order%20directing%20the%20police%20to%20complete%20the%20investigation%20within%20seven%20days%20and%20submit%20a%20detailed%20report.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%201999-%20batch%20IPS%20officer%2C%20Pandey%20has%20twice%20been%20suspended%20from%20his%20post%20in%20the%20past.%20First%2C%20for%20allegedly%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmumbaimirror.indiatimes.com%2Fmumbai%2Fother%2Fdeepak-pandeys-reinstatement-angers-women-ias-officers%2Farticleshow%2F15705936.cms%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etorturing%20his%20wife%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20and%20later%2C%20in%20connection%20with%20a%20sex%20scandal%20in%202008.%20Pandey%20was%20accused%20of%20sexually%20exploiting%20a%20teenage%20girl.%20The%20then%20home%20minister%20of%20Maharashtra%20R.R.%20Patil%20had%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmumbaimirror.indiatimes.com%2Fmumbai%2Fother%2Fips-officer-deepak-pandey-suspended%2Farticleshow%2F15800993.cms%23%3A~%3Atext%3DControversial%2520IPS%2520officer%2520Deepak%2520Pandey%2Cwas%2520unearthed%2520a%2520month%2520ago.%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eannounced%20his%20suspension%20on%20the%20floor%20of%20assembly%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20noted%20earlier%2C%20he%20is%20now%20tasked%20with%20prevention%20of%20crimes%20against%20women%20and%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711093405000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F02%2F11082632%2FImage6.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fpardhi-mumbai-police-minor-beating%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Police%20behaviour%20towards%20children%20of%20the%20Pardhi%20community%20in%20response%20to%20an%20allegation%20of%20thievery%20is%20a%20stark%20reminder%20of%20the%20extent%20to%20which%20law%20enforcement%20excesses%20plague%20marginalised%20communities.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fpardhi-mumbai-police-minor-beating%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Orry%20inspired%20outfits%20that%20exclaim%20Holi%20Hai!%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711093356000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108652883%2Cimgsize-106630.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fweb-stories%2Forry-inspired-9-colourful-outfits-that-exclaim-holi-hai%2Fphotostory%2F108652883.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F108652883.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EDiscover%209%20vibrant%20Holi%20outfits%20by%20Orry%20Awatramani%2C%20each%20bursting%20with%20colour%20and%20style%2C%20ready%20to%20make%20a%20statement%20this%20festive%20season!%20%23HoliSpecial%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fweb-stories%2Forry-inspired-9-colourful-outfits-that-exclaim-holi-hai%2Fphotostory%2F108652883.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Does%20the%20All-Powerful%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20Have%20a%20Director%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F29180215%2FThe-Wire-1.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20has%20been%20in%20the%20eye%20of%20a%20storm%20for%20excessive%20powers%20it%20appears%20to%20have%20amassed%2C%20and%20opposition%20parties%20have%20been%20up%20in%20arms%20over%20selective%20action%2C%20targeted%20action%20and%20no%20action%2C%20often%20depending%20on%20where%20those%20being%20attacked%20stand%2C%20politically.%20In%20just%20recent%20times%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99s%20Sukanya%20Shantha%20found%20that%20there%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-great-crossover-opposition-leaders-who-joined-the-bjp-after-action-by-central-agencies%5C%22%3Ewas%20a%20strong%20coincidence%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20leaders%20leaving%20for%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20and%20having%20faced%20%E2%80%98agency%E2%80%99%2C%20mostly%20ED%2C%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20data%20of%20bond%20donations%20and%20companies%20has%20emerged%2C%20multiple%20news%20reports%20have%20found%20on%20analysis%20that%20top%20electoral%20bond%20purchasers%20include%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Ftop-electoral-bond-purchasers-include-some-companies-that-were-raided-or-under-the-scanner%5C%22%3Ecompanies%20raided%20or%20under%20the%20scanner.%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0The%20pattern%20was%20so%20stark%20that%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20top%20leadership%2C%20so%20far%20embarrassed%20into%20silence%2C%20was%20forced%20to%20come%20out%20on%20being%20asked%20a%20question.%20Speaking%20at%20The%20India%20Today%20Conclave%202024%2C%20finance%20minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20tried%20to%20defend%20the%20Modi%20government%20and%20said%20it%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Chuge%20assumption%E2%80%9D%20that%20the%20money%20was%20given%20by%20firms%20after%20an%20ED%20visit.%20%E2%80%9CFor%20all%20you%20know%2C%20that%20money%20was%20given%20earlier%20and%20yet%2C%20we%20went%20knocking%20at%20their%20door.%20Am%20I%20making%20sense%3F%20No%3F!%E2%80%A6%20What%20if%20the%20companies%20gave%20the%20money%20and%20after%20that%2C%20we%20still%20went%20and%20knocked%20at%20their%20doors%20through%20the%20ED%E2%80%A6%20Is%20that%20a%20probability%20or%20not%3F%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fhuge-assumption-to-link-ed-raids-with-electoral-bond-purchases-says-finance-minister-nirmala-sitharaman%2Farticle67955597.ece%5C%22%3Eshe%20said%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20two%20years%20have%20been%20particularly%20eventful%20for%20the%20ED.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20controversial%20director%2C%20now%20only%20%E2%80%98acting%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20term%20of%20the%20last%20director%2C%20Sanjay%20K.%20Mishra%2C%20ended%20on%20September%2015%2C%202023.%20But%20not%20after%20fireworks%20in%20the%20top%20court%20as%20it%20forced%20his%20departure%2C%20terming%20his%20many%20extensions%20%E2%80%9Cillegal%E2%80%9D%20though%20later%20relenting%2C%20letting%20him%20continue%20till%20September%2015%2C%202023%20%E2%80%9Ctaking%20into%20consideration%20the%20larger%20public%20interest%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20government%20had%20insisted%20that%20it%20was%20important%20for%20Mishra%20to%20continue%20in%20his%20post%20because%20a%20country%20review%20of%20the%20UN%E2%80%99s%20Financial%20Action%20Task%20Force%20for%20India%20is%20currently%20underway%20%E2%80%93%20a%20claim%20that%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fsk-mishra-enforcement-directorate-fatf-evaluation%5C%22%3Eexperts%20had%20contested%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Despite%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20assertions%20on%20the%20importance%20of%20the%20ED%20director%E2%80%99s%20role%20in%20this%20process%2C%20it%20has%20not%20named%20Mishra%E2%80%99s%20successor%2C%20a%20full-time%20director%2C%20so%20far%2C%20continuing%20with%20one%20who%20is%20%E2%80%9Cacting%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CActing%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cextensions%E2%80%9D%20for%20constitutional%20posts%20or%20important%2C%20powerful%20positions%20is%20something%20the%20Modi%20government%20has%20been%20under%20tight%20scrutiny%20over.%20Vacancies%20have%20also%20been%20high%3B%20consider%20the%20three-year%20term%20Law%20Commission%20being%20vacant%20for%20over%20two%20and%20a%20half%20years%20or%20information%20commissioner%20vacancies%20lingering%20for%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20Navin%20is%20the%20acting%20director%20of%20the%20ED%20since%20Mishra%E2%80%99s%20term%20ended.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Appointments%20Committee%20of%20the%20Cabinet%20approved%20the%20%E2%80%9Cupgradation%20of%20Navin%20as%20special%20director%20of%20the%20Directorate%20of%20Enforcement%20(ED)%20in%20the%20rank%20and%20pay%20of%20additional%20secretary%2C%E2%80%9D%20in%20January%202024%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fcentre-upgrades-rank-of-ed-acting-chief-rahul-navin-to-additional-secretary-level%2Farticleshow%2F106657227.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20an%20order%3C%2Fa%3E%20issued%20by%20the%20Union%20personnel%20ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAn%20opposition%20skew%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20report%20by%20%3Cem%3EScroll%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%202022%20on%20the%20ED%E2%80%99s%20record%20of%20going%20after%20Opposition%20politicians%20pointed%20out%20the%20data%20and%20urgency%20with%20which%20the%20Opposition%20was%20gone%20after.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20the%20timing%20of%20ED%20investigations%20appears%20suspect%20in%20several%20cases%20involving%20the%20Opposition%2C%20conversely%2C%20it%20is%20hard%20not%20to%20notice%20the%20lack%20of%20similar%20alacrity%20in%20cases%20involving%20BJP%20leaders%E2%80%9D%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Farticle%2F1027571%2Fhow-the-modi-government-has-weaponised-the-ed-to-go-after-indias-opposition%5C%22%3Eit%20wrote.%3C%2Fa%3E%20Government%20data%20it%20cited%20revealed%20how%20cases%20under%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%20had%20zoomed%20since%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20investigation%20found%20that%2095%25%20of%20ED%20cases%20since%20the%20BJP%20came%20to%20power%20in%202014%20were%20against%20Opposition%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fpolitical-pulse%2Fkejriwal-arrest-bjp-liquor-policy-case-modi-9227288%2F%5C%22%3EA%20report%20by%3Cem%3E%20The%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%9Cshowed%20that%20between%202014%20and%20September%202022%2C%20121%20prominent%20leaders%20came%20under%20ED%20radar%2C%20115%20of%20them%20Opposition%20leaders%3B%20the%20list%20has%20grown%20since%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%20last%20year%20that%20ED%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fhow-the-enforcement-directorate-has-become-an-excessive-directorate%5C%22%3Eturned%20into%20an%20%E2%80%9CExcessive%20Directorate%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20vastly%20extending%20its%20own%20scope.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJudging%20ED%E2%80%99s%20powers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20amendments%20to%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%20(PMLA)%20were%20controversially%20upheld%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20last%20year%20by%20a%20bench%20headed%20by%20Justice%20A.M.%20Khanwilkar%E2%80%99s%20bench%2C%20two%20days%20before%20his%20retirement.%20As%20reported%20earlier%2C%20this%20bench%20upheld%20the%20wide%20powers%20of%20the%20ED%20to%20issue%20summons%2C%20record%20statements%2C%20make%20arrests%20and%20search%20and%20seize%20property.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20then%20a%20hearing%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20Special%20Bench%2C%20which%20agreed%20to%20revisit%20its%202022%20judgment%20upholding%20the%20PMLA.%20But%20it%20was%20doomed%20from%20the%20start%2C%20with%20the%20Union%20government%20questioning%20its%20legitimacy.%20Yet%2C%20Justice%20S.K.%20Kaul%2C%20who%20led%20the%20three-judge%20bench%20also%20comprising%20Justices%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%20and%20Bela%20M.%20Trivedi%2C%20sought%20to%20go%20ahead%20with%20the%20hearing%20initially%2C%20dismissing%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20contentions%20against%20the%20bench%E2%80%99s%20jurisdiction%20to%20hear%20the%20case%20with%20the%20hope%20that%20it%20would%20be%20able%20to%20complete%20the%20hearing%20and%20deliver%20a%20verdict%20before%20Justice%20Kaul%E2%80%99s%20last%20day%20in%20office%20on%20December%2016%2C%20prelude%20to%20his%20retirement%20on%20December%2025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20November%2023%2C%202023%2C%20the%20second%20day%20of%20the%20hearing%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20continued%20to%20obstruct%20the%20hearing.%20Solicitor%20General%20Tushar%20Mehta%2C%20who%20realised%20that%20he%20could%20not%20persuade%20the%20bench%20not%20to%20hear%20the%20case%2C%20sought%20more%20time%20to%20respond%20to%20the%20arguments%20of%20the%20petitioners%2C%20who%20he%20alleged%20had%20%E2%80%9Cexpanded%20their%20challenge%20to%20the%202022%20verdict%20beyond%20the%20issues%20they%20had%20initially%20raised%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20bench%20abandoned%20the%20endeavour.%20Now%2C%20the%20composition%20of%20the%20new%20bench%20to%20hear%20the%20case%2C%20to%20be%20constituted%20by%20the%20chief%20justice%2C%20will%20indicate%20whether%20the%20case%20will%20at%20all%20be%20heard%20by%20a%20larger%20bench.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20(retd)%20A.M.%20Khanwilkar%20was%20appointed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Df6JIM22q58A%26ab_channel%3DPresidentofIndia%5C%22%3Eas%20the%20Lokpal%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20March%2010%2C%202024%2C%20days%20before%20the%20model%20code%20of%20conduct%20kicked%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20there%20was%20also%20a%20petition%20filed%20by%2014%20opposition%20parties%20jointly%20alleging%20ED%20and%20CBI%20bias%2C%20but%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fsupreme-court-plea-opposition-political-parties-centre-investigating-agencies-ed-cbi-clamp-down-dissent-225564%5C%22%3Edecided%20to%20not%20hear%20it%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20year%20on%20April%205%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EED%E2%80%99s%20denial%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fhow-the-enforcement-directorate-has-become-an-excessive-directorate%5C%22%3Ein%20a%20response%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99s%20queries%20in%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20denied%20all%20allegations%20and%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9Cin%20all%20the%20cases%2C%20all%20actions%20taken%20by%20the%20ED%20have%20been%20approved%20by%20the%20concerned%20jurisdictional%20court%20from%20time%20to%20time.%20Moreover%2C%20as%20the%20questions%20posed%20by%20you%20pertain%20to%20sensitive%20cases%20and%20would%20amount%20to%20disclosing%20facts%20in%20pending%20cases%20where%20matter%20is%20sub-judice%20and%20also%20may%20pertain%20to%20disclosing%20investigating%20facts%2C%20which%20would%20not%20be%20proper.%20Wherever%2C%20the%20question%20regarding%20arrest%20etc.%20of%20accused%20have%20been%20raised%20in%20any%20judicial%20forum%20ED%20has%20adequately%20responded%20to%20the%20same%20by%20providing%20the%20correct%20information%20which%20have%20been%20accepted%20by%20the%20courts.%20It%20therefore%20appears%20that%20you%20have%20also%20not%20studied%20the%20applications%20filed%20by%20the%20accused%20in%20the%20other%20matters%20and%20replies%20filed%20by%20the%20ED%20and%20have%20posed%20unwarranted%20queries%20to%20ED.%20It%20may%20be%20so%20that%20you%20are%20being%20used%20by%20some%20persons%20with%20vested%20interest%20to%20propagate%20their%20biased%20views%20and%20also%20to%20elicit%20sensitive%20information%20from%20ED%20through%20you%20under%20the%20garb%20of%20investigative%20journalism.%20You%20are%20requested%20to%20go%20through%20the%20public%20record%20of%20the%20case%20as%20is%20available%20with%20various%20courts%2C%20the%20answers%20will%20be%20provided%20therein.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711093234000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F29180215%2FThe-Wire-1.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fdoes-the-all-powerful-enforcement-directorate-have-a-director%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Only%20%E2%80%98acting%E2%80%99.%20And%20there's%20a%20few%20other%20things%20y