uld%20stop%20the%20AAP%20leader%20from%20running%20the%20state%20from%20prison%2C%20the%20jail%20guidelines%20would%20make%20it%20extremely%20difficult.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20former%20law%20officer%20of%20Delhi's%20Tihar%20Jail%20says%20that%20an%20inmate%20can%20only%20hold%20two%20meetings%20in%20a%20week%2C%20which%20would%20make%20it%20difficult%20for%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20to%20carry%20out%20his%20responsibilities%20as%20Chief%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRunning%20a%20government%20from%20jail%20is%20not%20straightforward.%20The%20jail%20manual%20states%20that%20you%20can%20meet%20your%20family%2C%20friends%2C%20or%20associates%20only%20twice%20a%20week.%20So%20it%20will%20not%20be%20easy%20for%20him%20to%20govern%20with%20these%20restrictions%2C%26quot%3B%20Sunil%20Gupta%20tells%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20official%20says%20there%20is%20one%20way%20that%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20could%20carry%20on%20as%20Chief%20Minister.%20The%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20has%20the%20power%20to%20convert%20any%20building%20into%20a%20prison%2C%20and%20if%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20can%20convince%20him%20to%20put%20him%20under%20house%20arrest%20-%20it%20would%20help%20him%20be%20a%20part%20of%20the%20Delhi%20government's%20day-to-day%20functioning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Administrator%20has%20the%20authority%20to%20declare%20any%20building%20as%20a%20jail%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Gupta%20elucidated%2C%20drawing%20parallels%20with%20past%20instances%20where%20court%20complexes%20were%20designated%20as%20temporary%20jails.%20Such%20measures%2C%20he%20suggested%2C%20could%20potentially%20facilitate%20Arvind%20Kejriwal's%20governance%20from%20within%20confinement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Jharkhand%20Chief%20Minister%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjailed-hemant-soren-surrounded-by-cops-arrives-for-jharkhand-trust-vote-4996830%5C%22%3EHemant%20Soren%3C%2Fa%3E%20--%20who%20was%20arrested%20in%20January%20in%20connection%20with%20an%20alleged%20land%20scam%20--%20was%20taken%20into%20custody%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20after%20he%20met%20the%20Governor%20and%20stepped%20down%20from%20the%20post.%20The%20Chief%20Minister's%20post%20was%20handed%20over%20to%20party%20leader%20Champai%20Soren.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201998%2C%20when%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%2C%20then%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Bihar%2C%20got%20arrested%20in%20the%20fodder%20scam%20case%2C%20he%20handed%20over%20his%20charges%20to%20his%20wife%20Rabri%20Devi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal%20was%20arrested%20after%20he%20skipped%20summons%20for%20questioning%20for%20a%20ninth%20time%20in%20the%20liquor%20policy%20case%20and%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20refused%20to%20grant%20him%20protection%20from%20arrest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20arrest%20on%20Thursday%2C%20AAP's%20Atishi%2C%20who%20is%20currently%20number%202%20in%20the%20Delhi%20government%2C%20said%20that%20there%20will%20be%20no%20change%20in%20the%20party's%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BArvind%20Kejriwal%20is%20and%20will%20remain%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Delhi...%20there%20are%20no%20two%20ways%20about%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Atishi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20sources%20say%20the%20Union%20Home%20Ministry%20is%20examining%20the%20ramifications%20of%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20not%20resigning.%20Legal%20experts%20said%20the%20Centre%20may%20have%20to%20suspend%20or%20remove%20him%20from%20the%20post%20since%20he%20is%20a%20public%20servant.%20This%20is%20also%20the%20procedure%20that%20is%20followed%20for%20government%20officials%20who%20are%20arrested.%20They%20are%20immediately%20suspended%20from%20service%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20scrapped%20excise%20policy%2C%20introduced%20to%20bring%20an%20overhaul%20to%20the%20national%20capital's%20liquor%20business%2C%20promised%20a%20more%20modern%20shopping%20experience%20with%20discounts%20and%20offers.%20However%2C%20Delhi%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20Vinai%20Kumar%20Saxena's%20order%20to%20investigate%20alleged%20irregularities%20prompted%20the%20policy's%20cancellation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED's%20case%20is%20that%20the%20Delhi%20liquor%20policy%202021-22%20provided%20an%20exceptionally%20high-profit%20margin%20of%2012%20per%20cent%20for%20wholesalers%20and%20nearly%20185%20per%20cent%20for%20retailers.%20Of%20the%2012%20per%20cent%2C%206%20per%20cent%20was%20to%20be%20recovered%20from%20wholesalers%20as%20kickbacks%20for%20AAP%20leaders%2C%20and%20the%20%26quot%3BSouth%20Group%26quot%3B%20allegedly%20gave%20Rs%20100%20crore%20in%20advance%20to%20another%20accused%2C%20Vijay%20Nair%2C%20who%20was%20linked%20to%20the%20AAP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20key%20focus%20of%20the%20investigation%20into%20the%20Delhi%20liquor%20policy%20case%20was%20on%20an%20alleged%20network%20of%20middlemen%2C%20businessmen%20and%20politicians%20which%20the%20central%20agencies%20have%20called%20the%20%26quot%3BSouth%20Group%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20prominent%20AAP%20leaders%2C%20Manish%20Sisodia%20and%20Sanjay%20Singh%2C%20are%20already%20under%20judicial%20custody%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20case.%20Mr%20Sisodia%2C%20the%20former%20Delhi%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20was%20arrested%20by%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20on%20February%2026%20last%20year%2C%20while%20Mr%20Singh%2C%20a%20Rajya%20Sabha%20member%2C%20was%20arrested%20by%20the%20ED%20on%20October%205.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711090380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fjf7uum44_arvind-kejriwal_625x300_22_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcan-arvind-kejriwal-govern-delhi-after-arrest-what-jail-rules-say-5288034%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20has%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20will%20remain%20the%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20despite%20his%20arrest%20in%20the%20liquor%20policy%20case.%22%2C%22author%