tamorphopsia'%20describes%20transformation%20or%20distortion.%20According%20to%20%3Cem%3ENBC%20News%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20man%20suffering%20from%20PMO%20visited%20a%20lab%20at%20Dartmouth%20College%20describing%20what%20he%20has%20been%20experiencing%2C%20which%20allowed%20the%20medical%20experts%20to%20create%20a%20digital%20representation%20of%20what%20the%20warped%20faces%20look%20like%20to%20such%20a%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVictor%20Sharrah%20said%20the%20faces%20he%20sees%20have%20ears%2C%20noses%20and%20mouths%20stretched%20back%2C%20and%20there%20are%20deep%20grooves%20in%20their%20foreheads%2C%20cheeks%20and%20chins.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20first%20thought%20was%20I%20woke%20up%20in%20a%20demon%20world.%20You%20can't%20imagine%20how%20scary%20it%20was%2C%26quot%3B%20the%2059-year-old%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbcnews.com%2Fhealth%2Fhealth-news%2Fdisorder-man-sees-demonic-faces-rcna144533%5C%22%3Etold%20%3Cem%3ENBC%20News%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Clarksville%2C%20Tennessee%2C%20resident%20had%20a%20sharp%20vision%2C%20but%20things%20suddenly%20changed%20in%20November%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20friend%20then%20suggested%20he%20might%20have%20PMO%20and%20asked%20him%20to%20visit%20a%20doctor.%20Mr%20Sharrah%20felt%20the%20symptoms%20were%20a%20match%2C%20and%20he%20was%20formally%20diagnosed%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I'm%20looking%20at%20a%20person%2C%20that%20face%20is%20moving%2C%20it's%20talking%2C%20it's%20gesturing.%20So%20it%20really%20increases%20the%20effect%20of%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20man.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20strange%20fact%20about%20the%20neurological%20disorder%20is%20that%20the%20distortions%20appear%20only%20when%20Mr%20Sharrah%20sees%20people%20in%20person%20-%20not%20in%20photographs%20or%20through%20computer%20screens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20vivid%20descriptions%20allowed%20scientists%20to%20create%20a%20digital%20image%20of%20the%20distortions%2C%20something%20they%20had%20never%20been%20able%20to%20do%20before.%20The%20resulting%20images%20were%20published%20on%20Thursday%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thelancet.com%2Fjournals%2Flancet%2Farticle%2FPIIS0140-6736(24)00136-3%2Fabstract%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Lancet%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStudies%20say%20PMO%20symptoms%20subside%20after%20a%20few%20days%20or%20weeks%2C%20though%20in%20some%20cases%20they%20can%20linger%20for%20years.%20Mr%20Sharrah%20is%20still%20seeing%20the%20images%20after%20four%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20is%20prosopometamorphopsia%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20analysis%20of%20the%20symptoms%20of%20this%20rare%20disease%2C%20researchers%20suspect%20it%20is%20caused%20by%20dysfunction%20in%20the%20brain%20network%20that%20handles%20facial%20processing.%20However%2C%20they%20don't%20fully%20understand%20what%20triggers%20the%20condition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20patients%20were%20diagnosed%20with%20the%20disease%20after%20head%20trauma%2C%20stroke%2C%20epilepsy%20or%20migraines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20fewer%20than%20100%20published%20case%20reports%20of%20PMO.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711088760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F0afjn9io_prosopometamorphopsia-symptoms_625x300_22_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Frare-disorder-causes-man-to-see-demonic-faces-scary-5288301%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Victor%20Sharrah%20said%20the%20faces%20he%20sees%20have%20ears%2C%20noses%20and%20mouths%20stretched%20back%2C%20and%20there%20are%20deep%20grooves%20in%20their%20foreheads%2C%20cheeks%20and%20chins.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Frare-disorder-causes-man-to-see-demonic-faces-scary-5288301%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Frare-disorder-causes-m