%2C%20we%20had%20to%20separate%20the%20fleet%20for%20veg%20orders%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F31ru6X8cxWE%3Fsi%3DAqbPFPH3W7opi4DC%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20argument%2C%20on%20the%20%E2%80%98smell%E2%80%99%20of%20certain%20food%20disturbing%20others%2C%20has%20been%20called%20discriminatory%20based%20on%20caste%20and%20religion.%20%E2%80%9COne%20of%20the%20most%20important%20aspects%20of%20caste%20is%20food%20pollution%2C%E2%80%9D%20A.F.%20Mathew%2C%20a%20professor%20at%20IIM%20Kozhikode%2C%20told%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fto-solve-for-dietary-preference-of-100-vegetarians-zomato-introduces-a-pure-veg-fleet%2Farticle67969197.ece%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20will%20have%20to%20extend%20to%20whoever%20will%20deliver%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20continued.%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20if%20there%20is%20a%20Muslim%20driver%20bringing%20in%20a%20customer%E2%80%99s%20vegetarian%20food%3F%20%E2%80%A6%20Where%20is%20this%20going%3F%20Will%20Jains%20deliver%20for%20Jains%2C%20and%20Brahmins%20for%20Brahmins%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffood%2Findia-food-eating-vegetarianism%5C%22%3E2018%20article%20in%C2%A0%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20scholars%20Balmurli%20Natrajan%20and%20Suraj%20Jacob%20pointed%20out%20that%20%E2%80%9CThe%20extent%20of%20overall%20vegetarianism%20is%20much%20less%20than%20common%20claims%20and%20stereotypes%20suggest%3B%20survey%20estimates%20show%20that%20between%2023%25%20and%2037%25%20of%20the%20population%20of%20India%20is%20vegetarian.%20Thus%2C%20far%20from%20being%20a%20vegetari