0calm.%20He%20is%20a%20very%20good%20human%20being.%20I%20am%20extremely%20elated%20for%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20Ashwin%20backed%20the%20young%20opener%20to%20find%20success%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20off-spinner.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711082580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Flpccco3_dhoni-and-ashwin-ipl_625x300_22_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Fmustve-told-ruturaj-gaikwad-r-ashwins-big-talk-on-ms-dhonis-csk-captaincy-call-5287298%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ravichandran%20Ashwin%20shared%20his%20opinion%20on%20the%20CSK%20captaincy%20change%20that%20saw%20Ruturaj%20Gaikwad%20replacing%20MS%20Dhoni%20at%20the%20helm.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22BRS%3A%20Megha%20Engineering%20Is%20Top%20Donor%20to%20the%20Fourth-Largest%20Recipient%20of%20Electoral%20Bonds%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F22100910%2FGHLBJLxaAAAU_cV.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%2C%20or%20K.%20Chandrashekhar%20Rao%E2%80%99s%20BRS%20party%2C%20which%20held%20Hyderabad%20for%20two%20consecutive%20terms%20till%20the%20assembly%20elections%20in%202023%2C%20is%20among%20the%20top%20five%20beneficiaries%20of%20the%20electoral%20bond%20scheme.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20has%20been%20the%20fourth%20largest%20recipient%20of%20electoral%20bonds%2C%20nationally.%20Of%20the%20total%20of%20Rs%201%2C322%20crore%20it%20received%2C%20as%20per%20its%20own%20affidavit%20in%20a%20sealed%20cover%2C%20it%20is%20now%20established%20that%20Rs%20195%20crore%20came%20for%20the%20second%20largest%20buyer%20of%20bonds%2C%20Megha%20Engineering%20and%20Infrastructures%20Ltd%20(MEIL).%20MEIL%20is%20an%20infra%20company%20based%20in%20Hyderabad.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYashoda%20Super%20Speciality%20Hospital%20gave%20BRS%20Rs%2094%20crore.%20Chennai%20Greenwoods%20Private%20Limited%20gave%20BRS%20Rs%2050%20crore.%20Hetero%20Drugs%20and%20Labs%20too%20donated%20Rs%2050%20crore%20each.%20This%20came%20in%20one%20year%2C%202022.%20Dr%20Reddy%E2%80%99s%20Laboratories%20donated%20it%20Rs%2032%20crore.%20Divis%20Laboratories%2C%20Aurobindo%20Pharma%20Ltd%2C%20MSN%20Pharmachem%2C%20Hazelo%20Lab%2C%20Natco%20Pharma%2C%20Hetero%20Drugs%20and%20Biological%20E%20are%20among%20pharmaceutical%20firms%20who%20are%20significant%20donors.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20its%20submission%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%20it%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CElectoral%20bonds%20received%2C%20deposited%2C%20and%20credited%20to%20our%20party%E2%80%99s%20account%20from%20Oct%2011%2C%202018%2C%20to%20Sept%2030%2C%202023%2C%20totals%201%2C322%20crore.%20However%2C%20detailed%20particulars%20of%20the%20donors%20against%20each%20bond%20are%20not%20available%20with%20us%20as%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20scheme%20procedure%20has%20not%20provided%2Ffacilitated%20for%20capturing%20of%20the%20details%20of%20the%20donors%20of%20the%20bonds.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20April%2012%2C%202022%20BRS%20encashed%20268%20bonds%20each%20worth%201%20crore%2C%20the%20highest%20it%20encashed%20in%20a%20single%20day.%20The%20data%20has%20no%20purchaser%20marked%20for%20Rs%2023.55%20crore%20worth%20of%20bonds%20encashed%20by%20the%20BRS.%20This%20is%20presumed%20to%20be%20the%20amount%20paid%20and%20bought%20before%20April%2012%2C%202019%2C%20for%20which%20donors%20are%20yet%20to%20be%20identified%2C%20across%20parties.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKitex%20Group%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAn%20interesting%20name%20emerging%20as%20a%20donor%20to%20the%20BRS%2C%20of%20Rs%2025%20crore%20in%202023%20is%20the%20Kitex%20group%2C%20a%20garment%20major%20based%20in%20Kerala%2C%20which%20backed%20a%20political%20party%20called%20Twenty20%2C%20which%20AAP%E2%80%99s%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.firstpost.com%2Fpolitics%2Ftwenty20-party-arvind-kejriwal-ally-kitex-kizhakkambalam-10678821.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eannounced%20an%20alliance%20with%20in%202022%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20called%20the%20People%E2%80%99s%20Welfare%20Alliance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMorphing%20from%20the%20Telangana%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20to%20a%20party%20nursing%20national%20ambitions%20in%20these%20past%20years%2C%20BRS%20changed%20its%20name%20to%20the%20Bharatha%20Rashtra%20Samithi.%20Its%20profile%20grew%20as%20it%20contested%20elections%20in%20Maharashtra%20and%20became%20more%20prominent.%20This%20was%20a%20significant%20leap%20for%20a%20party%20formed%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20a%20specific%20movement%20calling%20for%20a%20separate%20Telangana%20state.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20have%20been%20patterns%20emerging%20between%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20raids%20and%20those%20by%20other%20agencies%20on%20leading%20companies%20who%20are%20buyers%20of%20bonds.%20In%20the%20case%20of%20BRS%2C%20ED%20had%20been%20pursuing%20the%20BRS%20founder%20and%20head%2C%20KCR%E2%80%99s%20daughter%2C%20MLC%20K.%20Kavitha%20in%20the%20alleged%20liquor%20scam%2C%20before%20arresting%20her%20two%20days%20ago.%20She%20is%20in%20ED%E2%80%99s%20custody%20at%20present.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20Thursday%20night%2C%20ED%20went%20and%20arrested%20another%20sitting%20chief%20minister%2C%20the%20second%20INDIA%20ally%20to%20be%20picked%20up%2C%20AAP%E2%80%99s%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20in%20a%20matter%20related%20to%20the%20same%20policy%20which%20has%20now%20been%20scrapped.%20Former%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20of%20Delhi%2C%20Manish%20Sisodia%20and%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Sanjay%20Singh%20are%20also%20in%20jail%20in%20the%20same%20matter.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711082429000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F22100910%2FGHLBJLxaAAAU_cV.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftelangana-brs-megha-kitex-electoral-bonds%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22BRS%20has%20received%20smaller%20amounts%20from%20other%20companies.%20An%20interesting%20name%20that%20has%20emerged%20is%20of%20Kitex%20Garments%2C%20which%20has%20formed%20a%20political%20party%2C%20Twenty20%20in%20Kerala.%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20announced%20an%20alliance%20with%20it%20in%202022.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftelangana-brs-megha-kitex-electoral-bonds%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Company%20of%20Businessman%20Who%20Turned%20Approver%20in%20Delhi%20Liquor%20Policy%20Case%20Donated%20Rs%205%20Crore%20to%20BJP%20Days%20After%20Arrest%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F22100846%2FUnknown.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EHyderabad-based%20businessman%20P.%20Sarath%20Chandra%20Reddy%E2%80%99s%20company%2C%20Aurobindo%20Pharma%20Limited%20%E2%80%93%20which%20was%20linked%20to%20the%20Delhi%20liquor%20policy%20case%20in%20which%20chief%20minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20was%20arrested%20on%20Thursday%20(March%2021)%20%E2%80%93%20donated%20electoral%20bonds%20worth%20Rs%205%20crore%20to%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20in%20November%202022%2C%20just%20five%20days%20after%20he%20was%20arrested%20in%20the%20case%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20information%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Farticle%2F1065604%2Fthe-curious-link-between-a-hyderabad-firms-electoral-bonds-to-bjp-and-the-delhi-liquor-policy-case%5C%22%3Ewas%20first%20revealed%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20reporter%20Jahnavi%20Reddy%20and%20Project%20Electoral%20Bond%2C%20after%20the%20Election%20Commission%20released%20the%20unique%20numbers%20associated%20with%20each%20electoral%20bond%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAurobindo%20Pharma%20Limited%20was%20founded%20by%20Sarath%20Reddy%E2%80%99s%20father%20P.V.%20Ram%20Prasad%20Reddy%2C%20and%20Sarath%20Reddy%20is%20one%20of%20its%20directors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Sarath%20Reddy%E2%80%99s%20case%20came%20up%20for%20bail%20in%20the%20Delhi%20high%20court%2C%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20did%20not%20oppose%20bail.%20In%20May%202023%2C%20the%20court%20granted%20him%20bail%20on%20medical%20grounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20June%202023%2C%20Sarath%20Reddy%20turned%20approver%20in%20the%20case.%20Two%20months%20later%2C%20the%20pharma%20company%20donated%20another%20Rs%2025%20crore%20to%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20Sarath%20Reddy%E2%80%99s%20arrest%2C%20the%20company%20had%20donated%20money%20to%20the%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20and%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20through%20electoral%20bonds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpposition%20leaders%20including%20Delhi%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20Manish%20Sisodia%20and%20BRS%20MLC%20K.%20Kavitha%20have%20been%20previously%20arrested%20in%20the%20case.%20Opposition%20parties%20have%20accused%20the%20Union%20government%20of%20using%20central%20agencies%20to%20stifle%20all%20dissent%20and%20political%20opposition%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711082363000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F22100846%2FUnknown.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcompany-of-businessman-who-turned-approver-in-delhi-liquor-policy-case-donated-rs-5-crore-to-bjp-days-after-arrest%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Aurobindo%20Pharma%20Limited%20was%20founded%20by%20Sarath%20Reddy's%20father%20P.V.%20Ram%20Prasad%20Reddy%2C%20and%20Sarath%20Reddy%20is%20one%20of%20its%20directors.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcompany-of-businessman-who-turned-approver-in-delhi-liquor-policy-case-donated-rs-5-crore-to-bjp-days-after-arrest%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%221%20Dead%2C%2030%20Feared%20Trapped%20As%20Bridge%20Under%20Construction%20Collapses%20In%20Bihar%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOne%20person%20was%20killed%20and%20several%20others%20trapped%20as%20an%20under-construction%20bridge%20collapsed%20in%20Bihar's%20Supaul.%20The%20bustling%20construction%20site%20near%20Maricha%20turned%20into%20a%20scene%20of%20chaos%20and%20devastation%20after%20the%20collapse%20at%20around%207am%20today%2C%20prompting%20urgent%20rescue%20efforts%20by%20local%20authorities%20and%20volunteers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAuthorities%20fear%20that%2030%20workers%20could%20still%20be%20trapped%20under%20the%20debris.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20reports%2C%20the%20bridge%20was%20being%20built%20at%20a%20cost%20of%20Rs%20984%20crore%20over%20the%20river%20Kosi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20accident%20bears%20an%20uncanny%20resemblance%20to%20the%20collapse%20of%20an%20under-construction%20bridge%20in%20Bihar's%20Bhagalpur%2C%20which%20had%20sparked%20a%20wr%20of%20words%20between%20the%20state%20government%20and%20the%20opposition%20BJP.%20The%20four-lane%20bridge%20constructed%20over%20the%20river%20Ganges%20had%20come%20crashing%20down%20like%20a%20house%20of%20cards.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bridge%20was%20supposed%20to%20link%20Bhagalpur%20and%20Khagaria%20districts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20under-construction%20bridge%2C%20a%20portion%20of%20which%20caved%20in%2C%20involved%20a%20cost%20of%20over%20Rs%201%2C700%20crore%20and%20was%20supposed%20to%20be%20completed%20by%202019.%20The%20foundation%20stone%20of%20the%20structure%20was%20laid%20in%20February%202014%2C%20by%20Chief%20Minister%20Nitish%20Kumar.%3C