ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ERLV-LEX-02%20Experiment%3A%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%F0%9F%87%AE%F0%9F%87%B3ISRO%20nails%20it%20again!%F0%9F%8E%AF%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnPushpak%20(RLV-TD)%2C%20the%20winged%20vehicle%2C%20landed%20autonomously%20with%20precision%20on%20the%20runway%20after%20being%20released%20from%20an%20off-nominal%20position.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%F0%9F%9A%81%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FIAF_MCC%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40IAF_MCC%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FIHNoSOUdRx%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FIHNoSOUdRx%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ISRO%20(%40isro)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fisro%2Fstatus%2F1770996593292136953%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%2022%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BISRO%20nails%20it%20again!%20Pushpak%20(RLV-TD)%2C%20the%20winged%20vehicle%2C%20landed%20autonomously%20with%20precision%20on%20the%20runway%20after%20being%20released%20from%20an%20off-nominal%20position%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20space%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EISRO%20said%20the%20mission%20successfully%20simulated%20the%20approach%20and%20high-speed%20landing%20conditions%20of%20RLV%20returning%20from%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20winged%20vehicle%2C%20called%20Pushpak%2C%20was%20lifted%20by%20an%20Indian%20Airforce%20Chinook%20helicopter%2C%20and%20was%20released%20from%204.5%20km%20altitude.%20After%20release%20at%20distance%20of%204km%20from%20the%20runway%2C%20Pushpak%20autonomously%20approached%20the%20runway%20along%20with%20cross%20range%20corrections.%20It%20landed%20precisely%20on%20the%20runway%20and%20came%20to%20a%20halt%20using%20its%20brake%20parachute%2C%20landing%20gear%20brakes%20and%20nose%20wheel%20steering%20system%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20experiment%20was%20the%20third%20flight%20of%20Pushpak%2C%20part%20of%20a%20test%20of%20its%20robotic%20landing%20ability%20in%20more%20complicated%20circumstances.%20It%20is%20expected%20to%20take%20many%20more%20years%20to%20deploy%20Pushpak%20operationally%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Pushpak%20launch%20vehicle%20is%20India's%20bold%20attempt%20to%20make%20access%20to%20space%20most%20affordable%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Somanath%20had%20earlier%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Pushpak%20being%20dropped%20from%20an%20Air%20Force%20helicopter%20as%20part%20of%20the%20test.%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Pushpak%20being%20dropped%20from%20an%20Air%20Force%20helicopter%20as%20part%20of%20the%20test.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fg0cn7dq_pushpak-experiment_625x300_22_March_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPushpak%20being%20dropped%20from%20an%20Air%20Force%20helicopter%20as%20part%20of%20the%20test.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20India's%20futuristic%20Reusable%20Launch%20Vehicle%2C%20where%20the%20most%20expensive%20part%2C%20the%20upper%20stage%2C%20which%20houses%20all%20the%20expensive%20electronics%2C%20is%20made%20reusable%20by%20bringing%20it%20back%20safely%20back%20to%20Earth.%20Later%2C%20it%20could%20even%20do%20refuelling%20of%20in-orbit%20satellites%20or%20retrieving%20satellites%20from%20orbit%20for%20refurbishment.%20India%20seeks%20to%20minimise%20space%20debris%20and%20Pushpak%20is%20one%20step%20towards%20that%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERVL%20flew%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%202016%20and%20successfully%20landed%20on%20a%20virtual%20runway%20in%20the%20Bay%20of%20Bengal.%20As%20per%20the%20plan%2C%20it%20sank%20in%20the%20sea%20and%20was%20never%20recovered.%20A%20second%20test%20was%20successfully%20conducted%20in%202023%20when%20winged%20rocket%20was%20dropped%20from%20air%20by%20a%20Chinook%20Helicopter%20for%20an%20autonomous%20landing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rocket%20draws%20its%20name%20from%20the%20'Pushpak%20Viman'%20mentioned%20in%20the%20Ramayana