0of%20Rs%2075.80%20crore%2C%20which%20included%20Avees%20Trading%E2%80%99s%20financial%20loss%20of%20Rs%2052%20crore.%20During%20this%20period%2C%20Avees%20Trading%20purchased%20electoral%20bonds%20worth%20Rs%2024%20crore.%20All%20of%20that%20went%20to%20the%20TMC.%20In%202021%2C%20it%20paid%20TMC%20Rs%2015%20crore%20and%20in%202023%2C%20Rs%206.5%20crore.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EConstruction%20firm%20Chennai%20Green%20Woods%20Private%20Limited%20donated%20TMC%20Rs%2040%20crore%20out%20of%20Rs%20105%20crore%20through%20electoral%20bonds.%20The%20company%2C%20operating%20out%20of%20Ramky%20Towers%20in%20Hyderabad%2C%20the%20official%20address%20of%20the%20Hyderabad%20based%20Ramky%20group%2C%20has%20made%20a%20one%20time%20donation%20to%20the%20party%20on%20January%205%2C%202022.%20On%20the%20same%20day%2C%20another%20company%20located%20in%20the%20same%20address%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Waste%20Management%20Pvt%20Ltd%20donated%20Rs%206%20crore%20to%20TMC.%20Ramky%20Towers%20is%20the%20official%20address%20of%20the%20Ramky%20group%2C%20which%20has%20been%20under%20ED%20and%20IT%20scanner%20for%20a%20long%20time.%20Four%20days%20later%2C%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Felections%2Fassembly-election-dates-full-schedule-punjab-uttar-pradesh-uttarakhand-goa-manipur-7713017%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EECI%20announced%20assembly%20elections%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3Ein%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Manipur%2C%20Punjab%2C%20Uttarakhand%2C%20and%20Goa.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPrarambh%20Securities%2C%20a%20little%20known%20stock%20brokering%20firm%20also%20paid%20TMC%20Rs%2038.75%20crore%20in%20January%202022.%20The%20Mumbai%20based%20firm%20also%20paid%20Rs%2033%20crore%20to%20BJP%2C%20Rs%205%20crore%20to%20Congress%20and%20Rs%202%20crore%20to%20Shivsena.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20least%20Rs%20135.crore%20of%20TMC%E2%80%99s%20electoral%20bonds%20came%20from%20Indian-made