%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBy%20a%20significant%20margin%2C%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20largest%20donor%20was%20Megha%20Engineering%2C%20based%20in%20Hyderabad%2C%20which%20contributed%20Rs%20584%20crore%20%E2%80%93%20out%20of%20the%20firm%E2%80%99s%20total%20bond%20purchases%20amounting%20to%20Rs%20966%20crore%20%E2%80%93%20between%202019%20and%202023.%20The%20company%20now%20owns%20a%20major%20stake%20in%20the%20TV9%20network.%20Another%20MEIL%20company%20Western%20UP%20Power%20Transmission%20Company%20Limited%20gave%20an%20additional%20Rs%2080%20crore.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20second%20place%20is%20QwikSupply%2C%20which%20is%20allegedly%20linked%20to%20the%20Reliance%20Group%2C%20at%20Rs%20375%20crore.%20The%20second%20highest%20donor%20for%20BJP%20were%20companies%20linked%20to%20Kolkata-based%20industrialist%20M.K.%20Jalan.%20In%20total%2C%20Madanlal%20Limited%2C%20Keventers%20Foodpark%2C%20MKJ%20enterprises%20and%20Sasmal%20gave%20Rs%20339.42%20crore%20to%20BJP.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20were%20no%20matching%20records%20for%20bond%20numbers%20which%20amounted%20to%20Rs%20466.31%20crore%20encashed%20by%20BJP%20among%20the%20data%20revealed%20on%20March%2021.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20per%20the%20numbers%20shared%20with%20EC%2C%20the%20BJP%20encashed%20Rs%201%2C505.4%20crores%20in%202019%2C%20when%20India%20went%20for%20general%20elections%20in%20April%20and%20May.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwho-were-the-top-buyers-of-electoral-bonds-paying%5C%22%3EWho%20Were%20the%20Top%20Buyers%20of%20Electoral%20Bonds%20Paying%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202019%2C%20the%20largest%20three%20donations%20through%20electoral%20bonds%20to%20BJP%20were%20as%20follows%3A%20Madanlal%20Limited%20contributed%20Rs%20175.5%20crore%2C%20Keventer%20Foodpark%20Infra%20Limited%20contributed%20Rs%20144.5%20crore%2C%20and%20Megha%20Engineering%20contributed%20Rs%20125%20crore.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20both%20Keventer%20and%20Madanlal%20Limited%20are%20linked%20to%20the%20same%20group%2C%20the%20two%20Jalan%20companies%20issued%20bonds%20worth%20Rs%20320%20crore%20in%20May%202019.%20Additionally%2C%20in%20October%20of%20the%20same%20year%2C%20another%20family-owned%20firm%2C%20MKJ%2C%20contributed%20an%20additional%20Rs%2014.42%20crore%20to%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20redemption%20of%20bonds%20by%20the%20ruling%20party%20experienced%20a%20significant%20drop%20to%20just%20Rs%2073.89%20crore%20in%202020.%20The%20top%20three%20donors%20for%20the%20BJP%20during%20that%20year%2C%20each%20contributing%20Rs%2010%20crore%2C%20were%20Apco%20Infratech%20Pvt%20Limited%2C%20Infina%20Finance%2C%20and%20an%20individual%20named%20Raju%20Kumar%20Sharma.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fflo.uri.sh%2Fvisualisation%2F17259376%2Fembed%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Interactive%20or%20visual%20content%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpublic.flourish.studio%2Fvisualisation%2F17259376%2F%3Futm_source%3Dembed%26utm_campaign%3Dvisualisation%2F17259376%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_top%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Made%20with%20Flourish%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpublic.flourish.studio%2Fresources%2Fmade_with_flourish.svg%5C%22%3E%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202021%2C%20incoming%20funds%20saw%20a%20substantial%20increase%20to%20Rs%20372%20crore%20as%20political%20activities%20resumed%20to%20pre-pandemic%20levels.%20The%20top%20three%20redemptions%20by%20the%20BJP%20were%20from%20Future%20Gaming%2C%20a%20lottery%20group%2C%20at%20Rs%2050%20crore%2C%20followed%20by%20Haldia%20Energy%20at%20Rs%2035%20crore%2C%20and%20Megha%20Engineering%20at%20Rs%2033%20crore.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20highest%20amount%20of%20bonds%20were%20redeemed%20in%202022%20when%20assembly%20elections%20were%20held%20in%20the%20states%20of%20Goa%2C%20Uttarakhand%2C%20Punjab%2C%20Manipur%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20Gujarat.%20According%20to%20the%20newly%20disclosed%20data%20%2C%20the%20BJP%20encashed%20Rs%201763.54%20crore%20in%202022%2C%20which%20was%20the%20highest%20amount%20for%20any%20year.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20top%20electoral%20bond%20donor%20in%202022%2C%20QwikSupply%2C%20contributed%20Rs%20325%20crore%20in%20two%20instalments%2C%20one%20in%20January%20and%20the%20other%20in%20November.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20other%20top%20donors%20for%20BJP%20through%20electoral%20bonds%20in%202022%20were%20Vedanta%20(Rs%20176.5%20crore)%20and%20Megha%20Engineering%20(Rs%20129%20crore).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202023%2C%20Megha%20Engineering%20upped%20its%20donation%20to%20BJP%20to%20Rs%20297%20crore%2C%20bringing%20it%20to%20the%20top%20of%20the%20list%20for%20that%20year.%20It%20was%20followed%20by%20Bharti%20Airtel%20at%20a%20distant%20second%20at%20Rs%2093%20crore%2C%20followed%20by%20Western%20UP%20Power%20Transmission%2C%20the%20MEIL%20group%20firm%2C%20at%20Rs%2080%20crore.%20It%20had%20been%20yet%20another%20bumper%20year%20in%20electoral%20bonds%20for%20BJP%20which%20redeemed%20Rs%201676.3%20crores.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20this%20year%2C%20BJP%20encashed%20Rs%20202%20crore%2C%20out%20of%20which%20Bharati%20Airtel%20gave%20Rs%2050%20crore%2C%20followed%20by%20Kolkata-based%20Rungta%20and%20Sons%20at%20Rs%2050%20crore%20too.%20Torrent%20Power%20was%20its%20third%20highest%20donor%20at%20Rs%2025%20crore.%20It%20had%20already%20encashed%20Rs%20202%20crore%20in%20electoral%20bonds%20before%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20deemed%20the%20whole%20process%20unconstitutional.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711077535000%2C%22v