mber%202019%2C%20the%20Press%20Information%20Bureau%20(PIB)%20established%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2Faboutfactchecke.aspx%5C%22%3Efact-check%20unit%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20the%20stated%20purpose%20of%20%E2%80%9Ctackling%20the%20issue%20of%20fake%20news%20pertaining%20to%20the%20Government%20of%20India%2C%20its%20various%20ministries%2C%20departments%2C%20public%20sector%20undertakings%2C%20and%20other%20central%20government%20organisations%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20body%20has%20been%20severely%20criticised%20for%20the%20government%20trying%20to%20conflate%20pro-government%20stories%20with%20%E2%80%98facts%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20main%20contention%20of%20independent%20media%20and%20others%20contesting%20the%20IT%20Rules%20giving%20the%20fact-check%20unit%20the%20power%20to%20be%20able%20to%20recommend%20the%20pulling%20down%20of%20stories%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20their%20%E2%80%98fact-checks%E2%80%99%20is%20that%20the%20PIB%2C%20a%20mouthpiece%20of%20the%20government%20of%20the%20day%2C%20cannot%20be%20relied%20upon%20to%20make%20decisions%20on%20%E2%80%98facts%E2%80%99%20or%20the%20truth%20and%20get%20material%20pulled%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Thursday%20(March%2021)%20stayed%20the%20establishment%20of%20a%20fact-check%20unit%2C%20till%20the%20Bombay%20high%20court%20which%20is%20hearing%20the%20matter%20gives%20its%20final%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%E2%80%99s%20stay%20will%20be%20operational%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fsupreme-court-stays-it-ministrys-notification-establishing-fact-check-unit-under-pib-to-identify-fake-news%2Farticle67975405.ece%5C%22%3Etill%20a%20third%20judge%20in%20the%20Bombay%20high%20court%20decides%20the%20question%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20%E2%80%9Cvalidity%20of%20provisions%20of%20the%20Rule%203(1)(b)(v)%20of%20the%20Information%20Technology%20(Intermediary%20Guidelines%20and%20Digital%20Media%20Ethics%20Code)%20Rules%2C%202021.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Internet%20Freedom%20Foundation%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Finternetfreedom%2Fstatus%2F1770446764438421505%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3Eon%20March%2020%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20the%20establishment%20of%20a%20government%20agency%20fact-check%20unit%20being%20set%20up%20once%20the%20election%20process%20was%20in%20full%20swing%20and%20the%20Model%20Code%20of%20Conduct%20in%20place%2C%20as%20something%20that%20%E2%80%9Ccould%20vastly%20affect%20the%20nature%20of%20free%20speech%20on%20the%20internet%20as%20it%20holds%20the%20potential%20to%20be%20(mis)used%20for%20proactive%20censorship%2C%20most%20importantly%20in%20the%20context%20of%20dissent.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20aside%20the%20merits%20of%20setting%20it%20up%2C%20the%20fact-check%20unit%20has%20had%20a%20chequered%20past.%20Here%20are%20at%20least%20five%20instances%20when%20the%20PIB%E2%80%99s%20fact-checking%20arm%20got%20it%20wrong%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFirstly%2C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20in%20May%202020%2C%20the%20PIB%20dubbed%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitical-economy%2Fmodis-monogrammed-suit-rajkot-ventilator-vijay-rupani%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20as%20%E2%80%9Cfactually%20incorrect%E2%80%9D.%20The%20report%20suggested%20links%20between%20top%20political%20leaders%20and%20Rameshkumar%20Virani%2C%20an%20influential%20businessman%20who%20had%20stakes%20in%20Jyoti%20CNC%2C%20the%20company%20manufacturing%20Dhaman-1%20ventilators%20during%20the%20ongoing%20COVID-19%20health%20crisis.%20These%20ventilators%20were%20found%20to%20be%20substandard%20by%20doctors%20in%20Gujarat%20and%20the%20Puducherry%20government.%20Later%20on%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%E2%80%99s%3C%2Fem%3E%20claims%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newslaundry.com%2F2020%2F05%2F26%2Fthe-embarrassment-that-is-pib-fact-check-who-fact-checks-this-fact-checker%5C%22%3Efound%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20have%20been%20correct.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESecond%2C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20on%20June%202%2C%202020%2C%20the%20PIB%E2%80%99s%20fact-check%20unit%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPIBFactCheck%2Fstatus%2F1267866492298645505%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20reports%20claiming%20that%20Chinese%20troops%20had%20entered%20the%20Indian%20side%20of%20the%20Line%20of%20Actual%20Control%20were%20a%20%E2%80%9Cmisrepresentation%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20defence%20minister%E2%80%99s%20statements.%20However%2C%20two%20months%20later%2C%20a%20document%20from%20the%20defence%20ministry%20conceded%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessworld.in%2Farticle%2FDefence-Ministry-admits-transgressions-by-Chinese-Army-in-Eastern-Ladakh%2F06-08-2020-305595%2F%5C%22%3Etransgression%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20indeed%20happened.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EClaim%3A%20Raksha%20Mantri%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Frajnathsingh%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40rajnathsingh%3C%2Fa%3E%20admitted%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FCNNnews18%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40CNNnews18%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Chinese%20soldiers%20crossed%20Indian%20side%20of%20LAC%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFact%3A%20The%20Minister%20was%20referring%20to%20differing%20perceptions%20of%20LAC%20%26amp%3B%20presence%20of%20Chinese%20troops%20It%20is%20being%20misinterpreted%20as%20if%20Chinese%20troops%20entered%20Indian%20side%20of%20LAC%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FXews6Ba1bq%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FXews6Ba1bq%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20PIB%20Fact%20Check%20(%40PIBFactCheck)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPIBFactCheck%2Fstatus%2F1267866492298645505%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJune%202%2C%202020%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it%20later%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fmod-takes-down-report-on-chinese-transgressions-into-indian-territory%2Farticle32284188.ece%5C%22%3Etook%20down%3C%2Fa%3E%20this%20report.%20According%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20report%20said%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20present%20situation%20arising%20from%20%E2%80%98unilateral%20aggression%E2%80%99%20by%20China%20continues%20to%20be%20sensitive%2C%20requiring%20close%20monitoring%20and%20prompt%20action%20brd%20on%20the%20evolving%20situation%2C%20and%20the%20present%20stand-off%20%E2%80%9Cis%20likely%20to%20be%20prolonged.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThird%2C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20during%20the%20ongoing%20Manipur%20violence%2C%20a%20story%20was%20published%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fmanipur-bsf-jawan-compensation%5C%22%3Eon%20a%20BSF%20jawan%E2%80%99s%20family%20not%20receiving%20compensation%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20he%20was%20killed%20in%20the%20violence%2C%20as%20promised%20by%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20PIB%20fact-check%20unit%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPIBFactCheck%2Fstatus%2F1698271253843399055%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3Esaid%20on%20X%3C%2Fa%3E%20(formerly%20Twitter)%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Cclaim%20is%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FFake%3Fsrc%3Dhashtag_click%5C%22%3E%23Fake%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20said%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Cfamily%20of%20late%20BSF%20Jawan%20received%20the%20entitled%20compensation%20from%20Golden%20Jubilee%20Seema%20Prahari%20Kalyan%20Kavach%20Yojana%20of%20Rs%2016%20lakh.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20in%20its%20report%2C%20had%20specifically%20mentioned%20the%20unpaid%20compensation%20was%20due%20to%20the%20dead%20jawan%E2%80%99s%20family%20from%20the%20Manipur%20state%20government%20and%20the%20Union%20government%2C%20as%20per%20the%20announcement%20made%20by%20Shah%20on%20June%201%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENote%20that%20the%20Golden%20Jubilee%20Seema%20Prahari%20Kalyan%20Kavach%20Yojana%20is%20a%20%3Cstrong%3Egroup%20insurance%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20pay-out%20to%20the%20family%2C%20not%20the%20%3Cstrong%3Ecompensation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20for%20death%20during%20the%20ongoing%20violence%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20story%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%E2%80%99s%3C%2Fem%3E%20correspondent%20clearly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fmanipur-bsf-jawan-compensation%5C%22%3Ementioned%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Ranjit%20Yadav%E2%80%99s%20wife%20had%20approached%20the%20government%20of%20Manipur%20twice%2C%20and%20she%20didn%E2%80%99t%20receive%20any%20compensation%20from%20them%20(till%20the%20time%20of%20filing%20the%20report).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20story%20specifically%20referred%20to%20no%20compensation%20from%20both%20the%20state%20government%20or%20from%20the%20Union%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reference%20is%20to%20what%20should%20have%20followed%20from%20the%20Union%20home%20minister%E2%80%99s%20promises%20in%20his%20press%20conference%20on%20June%201%2C%202023%2C%20where%20he%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D8m9jUIgwkzU%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E(time%20stamp%20%E2%80%93%208%3A20)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20those%20who%20lost%20their%20lives%20would%20receive%20Rs%205%20lakh%20in%20compensation%20from%20the%20Manipur%20government%20and%20Rs%205%20lakh%20from%20the%20Union%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PIB%20fact-check%20unit%20ignored%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fvifdatabase.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F05%2Freport-no-203.pdf%5C%22%3EGolden%20Jubilee%20Seema%20Prahari%20Kalyan%20Kavach%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20not%20compensation%2C%20but%20a%20group%20insurance%20scheme%2C%20as%20defined%20in%20official%20documents%2C%20for%20%E2%80%9Crisk%20to%20the%20lives%20of%20BSF%20troops%20while%20on%20duty.%E2%80%9D%20It%20is%20an%20internal%20insurance%20run%20by%20the%20paramilitary%20force.%20Jawans%20contribute%20to%20it.%20Listed%20under%20benefits%20on%20the%20BSF%20website%2C%20operational%20death%20cases%20should%20entitle%20the%20jawans%20to%20Rs%2040%20lakhs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFourth%2C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20in%202020%2C%20a%20news%20story%20was%20widely%20reported%20saying%20that%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Special%20Task%20Force%20had%20directed%20its%20personnel%20and%20their%20family%20members%20to%20delete%2052%20Chinese%20applications%20from%20their%20mobile%20phones%20for%20security%20reasons.%20PIB%20claimed%20that%20these%20reports%20were%20%E2%80%9Cfalse%E2%80%9D.%20However%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fpib-fact-check-blunders-again-declares-up-polices-advisory-on-chinese-apps-as-fake-news%5C%22%3Esubsequent%20probes%3C%2Fa%3E%20showed%20that%20it%20was%20the%20PIB%20that%20had%20got%20it%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFifth%2C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20in%202023%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20published%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fout-of-nearly-1-2-lakh-queries-in-3-years-pibs-fact-check-unit-acted-on-1223%5C%22%3Ean%20article%3C%2Fa%3E%20discussing%20the%20methodology%20and%20performance%20of%20the%20PIB%2C%20quoting%20facts%20and%20figures%20derived%20from%20a%20Right%20to%20Information%20response%20that%20the%20PIB%20itself%20had%20issued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20PIB%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Funcategorised%2Fpib-fact-check-unit-claims-our-article-on-its-work-is-misleading-five-reasons-why-it-is-wrong%5C%22%3Efound%20fault%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20this%20report%2C%20coming%20up%20with%20updated%20numbers%20and%20facts%20that%20were%20absent%20from%20its%20own%20reply.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDeebakar%20Majumder%20is%20an%20intern%20with%20%3C%2Fem%3EThe%20Wire.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711071030000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%