C%22%3E%20%E2%80%9Cwitch%20hunting%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20the%20opposition%20with%20its%20unbridled%20powers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fexpress-exclusive%2Fsince-2014-4-fold-jump-in-ed-cases-against-politicians-95-per-cent-are-from-opposition-8163060%2F%5C%22%3Efour-fold%20jump%20in%20ED%20cases%20since%202014%3C%2Fa%3E%3B%2095%25%20of%20those%20cases%20are%20against%20opposition%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20agency%20itself%20has%20been%20functioning%20under%20acting%20director%20Rahul%20Navin%20since%20September%202023%20with%20the%20Centre%20yet%20to%20find%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fon-ed-chief-sanjay-mishras-last-day-no-decision-yet-on-his-successor%5C%22%3Ereplacement%20for%20Sanjay%20Kumar%20Mishra.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMishra%20was%20appointed%20director%20in%202018%20for%20two%20years%20as%20his%20term%20was%20controversially%20extended%20by%20the%20Union%20government.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20called%20his%20extension%20%E2%80%9Cillegal%E2%80%9D%20but%20later%20allowed%20him%20to%20continue%20till%20September%2015%2C%202023%20%E2%80%9Ctaking%20into%20consideration%20the%20larger%20public%20interest%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711043292000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F23151422%2FScreenshot-2024-02-23-at-3.13.48.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Farvind-kejriwal-arrest-second-sitting-cm-lok-sabha-polls%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20arrest%20came%20shortly%20after%20the%20Election%20Commission%20published%20all%20data%2C%20including%20unique%20numbers%20relating%20to%20electoral%20bonds%2C%20on%20its%20website.%20The%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20has%20called%20Kejriwal%E2%80%99s%20arrest%20a%20%E2%80%98political%20conspiracy%E2%80%99%20and%20moved%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20sought%20an%20urgent%20hearing.