ransactions-124032101085_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20Double%20Murder%20and%20an%20Encounter%20in%20Budaun%20Spark%20Political%20Controversy%20in%20UP%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F21210036%2Fimage-1994.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20brutal%20murder%20of%20two%20minor%20Hindu%20boys%2C%20brothers%20aged%20six%20and%2011%2C%20allegedly%20by%20a%20Muslim%20barber%2C%20followed%20by%20his%20subsequent%20killing%20by%20police%20within%20a%20few%20hours%20of%20the%20incident%20in%20Budaun%2C%20has%20taken%20a%20political%20turn%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20ahead%20of%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20double-murder%20has%20led%20to%20widespread%20outrage%20as%20photos%20of%20the%20two%20murdered%20children%20were%20widely%20shared%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20incident%20has%20also%20triggered%20a%20political%20controversy%20in%20the%20state%20after%20the%20ruling%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20MP%20from%20Budaun%2C%20Sanghamitra%20Maurya%2C%20accused%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%E2%80%99s%20candidate%20Shivpal%20Yadav%20of%20having%20alleged%20links%20to%20the%20brutal%20killing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaurya%20also%20accused%20Yadav%20of%20being%20the%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9Csutradhar%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%20(facilitator%20or%20orchestrator)%20of%20the%20Muzaffarnagar%20riots%20in%202013%20and%20the%20Mathura%20Jawahar%20Bagh%20incident%20in%202016%2C%20both%20of%20which%20occurred%20under%20the%20SP%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SP%2C%20represented%20by%20its%20district%20president%20Ashish%20Yadav%2C%20has%20written%20to%20the%20district%20election%20officer%20and%20district%20police%20chief%2C%20accusing%20Maurya%20and%20the%20BJP%20of%20attempting%20to%20polarise%20voters%20along%20communal%20lines%20through%20this%20incident%20and%20violating%20the%20Model%20Code%20of%20Conduct.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20SP%20cited%20the%20incident%20as%20evidence%20of%20failed%20law%20and%20order%20in%20the%20state%20under%20the%20BJP%20government%2C%20leaders%20of%20the%20ruling%20party%20celebrated%20the%20killing%20of%20the%20accused%20person%20Sajid%20in%20an%20alleged%20%E2%80%9Cencounter%E2%80%9D%20within%20three%20hours%20of%20the%20murder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20double-murder%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20evening%20of%20March%2019%2C%20tension%20gripped%20parts%20of%20Budaun%20after%20a%20barber%20identified%20as%20Sajid%20entered%20the%20house%20of%20a%20Hindu%20family%20in%20Sundarnagar%20Baba%20Colony%20and%20used%20a%20knife%20to%20slit%20the%20throats%20of%20two%20brothers%20on%20the%20terrace.%20A%20third%20brother%2C%20also%20a%20minor%2C%20managed%20to%20run%20downstairs%20and%20escape.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20boy%20later%20recounted%20to%20media%20personnel%20that%20the%20accused%20Sajid%2C%20who%20operated%20a%20salon%20in%20the%20area%2C%20had%20come%20to%20their%20house%20and%20led%20his%20brothers%20upstairs%20where%20he%20killed%20them.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20tried%20to%20attack%20me%20too%2C%20but%20I%20pushed%20away%20his%20knife%2C%20pushed%20him%2C%20and%20ran%20downstairs%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20boy.%20He%20said%20he%20suffered%20injuries%20on%20the%20back%20of%20his%20head%20and%20hand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20are%20investigating%20the%20motive%20behind%20the%20crime%20but%20have%20not%20found%20any%20past%20disputes%20between%20the%20two%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mother%20of%20the%20minors%20informed%20local%20media%20that%20Sajid%20had%20visited%20their%20house%20under%20the%20guise%20of%20asking%20for%20money%20to%20pay%20for%20hospital%20expenses%20where%20his%20pregnant%20wife%20was%20admitted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20family%20also%20alleged%20that%20Sajid%E2%80%99s%20brother%2C%20Javed%2C%20was%20complicit%20in%20the%20murder%20and%20was%20waiting%20outside%20the%20house.%20On%20March%2021%2C%20Javed%20surrendered%20before%20police%20in%20Bareilly%20district%20and%20was%20taken%20into%20custody.%20The%20police%20had%20declared%20a%20bounty%20on%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20Budaun%20Alok%20Priyadarshi%20said%20that%20Javed%20was%20the%20second%20accused%20in%20the%20case%20and%20surrendered%20due%20to%20police%20pressure%20and%20the%20bounty%20declared%20against%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20talking%20to%20the%20officers%20%5Bin%20Bareilly%5D%2C%20our%20team%20is%20bringing%20him%20back.%20Further%20action%20will%20be%20taken%20after%20questioning%20him%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Priyadarshi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20Javed%20surrendered%20to%20the%20police%2C%20a%20video%20emerged%20on%20social%20media%20showing%20him%20claiming%20that%20he%20was%20at%20home%20when%20the%20incident%20took%20place%20and%20that%20his%20family%20had%20friendly%20terms%20with%20the%20victim%E2%80%99s%20family.%20However%2C%20he%20could%20not%20explain%20why%20Sajid%20committed%20the%20murder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPriyadarshi%20said%20that%20they%20are%20investigating%20why%20Sajid%2C%20despite%20getting%20the%20Rs%205%2C000%20he%20asked%20from%20the%20victim%E2%80%99s%20mother%2C%20committed%20the%20murders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20a%20mob%20set%20ablaze%20a%20shop%20belonging%20to%20Sajid%20after%20the%20news%20of%20the%20double-murder%20broke%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20leaders%20claimed%20that%20Sajid%E2%80%99s%20encounter%20prevented%20the%20situation%20from%20escalating%20into%20a%20communal%20riot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERakesh%20Singh%2C%20inspector%20general%20of%20Bareilly%20Range%2C%20said%20that%20after%20committing%20the%20murders%2C%20Sajid%2C%20who%20was%20seen%20escaping%20in%20blood-stained%20clothes%2C%20was%20intercepted%20near%20a%20jungle%20area%20by%20the%20Special%20Operations%20Group%20of%20the%20police%20and%20the%20local%20police%20station%20team.%20When%20the%20police%20reached%20the%20scene%2C%20he%20allegedly%20fired%20at%20the%20police%20and%20tried%20to%20escape%2C%20said%20Singh.%20Sajid%20was%20killed%20in%20retaliatory%20firing%20by%20the%20police%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20have%20said%20that%20they%20recovered%20a%20country-made%20pistol%20from%20the%20accused%20as%20well%20as%20the%20murder%20weapon%2C%20believed%20to%20be%20a%20knife.%20How%20the%20accused%20obtained%20the%20pistol%20and%20why%20he%20chose%20the%20knife%20as%20a%20murder%20weapon%20still%20remain%20unclear.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBudaun%E2%80%99s%20electoral%20significance%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20the%20murder%20case%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20major%20talking%20point%20in%20the%20state%2C%20due%20to%20Budaun%E2%80%99s%20electoral%20significance%2C%20which%20is%20a%20traditional%20SP%20stronghold.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20MP%20Maurya%20and%20Aditya%20Yadav%2C%20son%20of%20the%20SP%20candidate%20Shivpal%20Yadav%2C%20have%20already%20visited%20the%20home%20of%20the%20aggrieved%20family%20to%20express%20solidarity%20amidst%20their%20campaigning%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERamgopal%20Yadav%2C%20SP%E2%80%99s%20national%20general%20secretary%2C%20on%20Wednesday%20(March%2020)%2C%20pointed%20fingers%20at%20the%20ruling%20BJP%2C%20when%20asked%20for%20a%20comment%20by%20reporters.%20%E2%80%9CBJP%20people%20always%20create%20violence%20during%20elections%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20comment%20triggered%20a%20sharp%20response%20from%20the%20BJP%20whose%20leaders%20and%20lawmakers%20accused%20the%20SP%20of%20politicising%20the%20crime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESP%20president%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20said%20the%20%E2%80%9CBJP%20cannot%20hide%20its%20failures%20through%20the%20encounter.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20uncle%20and%20senior%20SP%20leader%20Shivpal%20Yadav%2C%20who%20is%20contesting%20from%20Budaun%2C%20said%20the%20incident%20showed%20that%20the%20law%20and%20order%20of%20the%20state%20had%20fully%20failed.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20encounter%20happened.%20But%20how%20will%20the%20truth%20of%20the%20case%20be%20unravelled%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanghamitra%20Maurya%2C%20the%20sitting%20BJP%20MP%2C%20who%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20declared%20a%20candidate%20in%20this%20election%2C%20publicly%20supported%20Sajid%E2%80%99s%20police%20encounter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20she%20also%20used%20the%20incident%20to%20train%20her%20guns%20at%20Shivpal%20Yadav%20and%20alleged%2C%20without%20any%20factual%20backing%2C%20that%20she%20suspected%20Shivpal%20to%20be%20the%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9Csutradhar%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20the%20Budaun%20incident%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20communal%20violence%20in%20Muzaffarnagar%20in%202013%20and%20the%20Mathura%20violence%20in%202016.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20talk%20about%20riots%2C%20SP%20leaders%20say%20that%20BJP%20wants%20to%20win%20elections%20by%20inciting%20riots.%20I%20want%20to%20say%20this%20clearly%20that%20the%20BJP%20has%20been%20at%20the%20Centre%20for%2010%20years%20and%20eight%20years%20in%20the%20state%2C%20till%20date%20not%20a%20single%20riot%20has%20taken%20place%20under%20the%20BJP.%20When%20the%20SP%20was%20in%20power%20from%202012%20to%202017%2C%20a%20record%20300%20riots%20took%20place.%20In%20those%20300%20riots%2C%20the%20two%20most%20important%20ones%20were%20Muzaffarnagar%20and%20Mathura%20riots.%20In%20both%20incidents%20the%20sutradhar%20was%20the%20SP%E2%80%99s%20candidate%20in%20Budaun%2C%E2%80%9D%20alleged%20Maurya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20MP%20further%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CAnd%20his%20statement%20after%20coming%20to%20Budaun%20that%20%E2%80%98I%20am%20here%2C%20now%20everything%20will%20be%20fine%E2%80%99%2C%20in%20a%20way%20creates%20a%20doubt.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20has%20tried%20to%20build%20a%20wall%20of%20religion%20in%20some%20way.%20That%20such%20an%20incident%20took%20place%20within%20three%20to%20four%20days%20of%20him%20coming%20here%2C%20in%20some%20way%20his%20role%20also%20comes%20under%20suspicion%E2%80%A6because%20he%20made%20such%20a%20statement%20and%20levelled%20allegations%20against%20the%20BJP%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Maurya%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SP%2C%20in%20official%20complaints%20to%20the%20police%20and%20district%20magistrate%2C%20accused%20Maurya%20of%20trying%20to%20spread%20hatred%20and%20divide%20the%20society.%20Maurya%20made%20%E2%80%9Cmisleading%20and%20baseless%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Ccommunal%E2%80%9D%20remarks%20against%20Shivpal%20Yadav%20as%20part%20of%20a%20conspiracy%2C%20the%20party%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20purpose%20of%20this%20comment%20is%20to%20hold%20democracy%20hostage%20and%20influence%20the%20results%20of%20the%20election.%20It%20is%20clear%20that%20a%20cruel%20attempt%20is%20being%20made%20to%20influence%20the%20Budaun%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%202024%20through%20these%20machinations.%20This%20entire%20comment%20is%20extremely%20undemocratic%20and%20shameful%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20SP%20said%20in%20its%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20chief%20Mayawati%2C%20who%20has%20been%20politically%20inactive%2C%20also%20condemned%20the%20murders.%20%E2%80%9CStrict%20legal%20action%20is%20necessary%20against%20the%20culprits%20so%20that%20the%20law%20and%20order%20situation%20does%20not%20get%20worse%2C%20especially%20during%20election%20time.%20%5BIt%20should%20be%20ensured%20that%5D%20politics%20does%20not%20take%20place%20over%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mayawati%20said%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20Budaun%20witnessed%20a%20close%20electoral%20contest%20with%20the%20BJP%20defeating%20SP%E2%80%99s%20Dharmendra%20Yadav.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20time%2C%20by%20fielding%20Shivpal%20Yadav%20from%20Budaun%2C%20the%20SP%20has%20raised%20the%20stakes%20in%20the%20constituency%2C%20which%20is%20set%20to%20go%20to%20polls%20in%20the%20third%20phase%20on%20May%207.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELok%20Sabha%20polls%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20will%20be%20held%20in%20seven%20phases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20is%20yet%20to%20declare%20a%20candidate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanghamitra%20Maurya%E2%80%99s%20father%20Swami%20Prasad%20Maurya%20recently%20quit%20the%20SP%20to%20form%20his%20own%20outfit.%20He%20had%20quit%20the%20BJP%20in%202022%20but%20his%20daughter%20continued%20to%20serve%20as%20a%20BJP%20MP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBJP%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20believe%20in%20riots.%20BJP%20believes%20in%20bhaichara%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said%20in%20Budaun%2C%20following%20the%20news%20of%20murders.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711035113000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F21210036%2Fimage-1994.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fa-double-murder-and-an-encounter-in-budaun-spark-political-controversy-in-up%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20the%20murder%20case%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20major%20talking%20point%20in%20the%20state%2C%20due%20to%20Budaun's%20electoral%20significance.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fa-double-murder-and-an-encounter-in-budaun-spark-political-controversy-in-up%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Prince%20Harry%E2%80%99s%20call%20bugged%2C%20Princess%20Diana%E2%80%99s%20messages%20accessed%20by%20tabloid%20papers'%2C%20Lawyers%20allege%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711031720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108684181%2Cimgsize-31526.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Fprince-harrys-call-bugged-princess-dianas-messages-accessed-by-tabloid-papers-lawyers-allege%2Farticleshow%2F108684100.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%