Preventing%20fires%20through%20community%20participation%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20THF%E2%80%99s%20intervention%2C%20Pritam%2C%20like%20many%20other%20volunteers%2C%20was%20provided%20comprehensive%20training%20to%20tackle%20forest%20fires.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20he%20was%20better%20equipped%20and%20prepared%20for%20any%20untoward%20incidents%20similar%20to%20those%20that%20occurred%20in%202022%20and%20was%20able%20to%20respond%20to%20the%20emergency%20and%20control%20potential%20fire%20incidents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20educated%20on%20how%20to%20implement%20local%20mitigation%20strategies%20to%20effectively%20control%20any%20forest%20fire.%20We%20were%20provided%20with%20firefighting%20kits%20that%20included%20a%20set%20of%20different%20types%20of%20fire%20rakes%2C%20a%20modified%20sickle%2C%20a%20shovel%2C%20a%20fire%20beater%2C%20and%20a%20tool%20kit%20bag.%20Training%20was%20provided%20on%20fire%20line%20development%2C%20biomass%20management%2C%20safety%20measures%20during%20fire%20dousing%2C%20and%20uses%20of%20the%20various%20equipment%20that%20were%20provided%20to%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20how%20he%20responds%20to%20the%20emergency%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20first%20inform%20the%20forest%20department%20about%20any%20forest%20fires%20that%20occur%20in%20the%20area.%20Meanwhile%2C%20we%20start%20clearing%20broad%20strips%20of%20land%20of%20all%20inflammable%20material%20like%20dry%20leaves%20and%20fodder%20so%20that%20fire%20does%20not%20extend%20from%20one%20area%20to%20another.%20After%20making%20forest%20lines%2C%20we%20also%20throw%20sand%20to%20extinguish%20the%20fire.%20However%2C%20if%20the%20fire%20is%20on%20a%20large%20scale%2C%20we%20try%20to%20prevent%20it%20from%20spreading%20further%20rather%20than%20extinguishing%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fhans-2-1-1711021807.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Following%20THF%E2%80%99s%20intervention%2C%20many%20volunteers%20were%20provided%20comprehensive%20training%20to%20tackle%20forest%20fires.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fhans-2-1-1711021807.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fhans-2-1-1711021807-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fhans-2-1-1711021807-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fhans-2-1-1711021807-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fhans-2-1-1711021807-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345443%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EFollowing%20THF%E2%80%99s%20intervention%2C%20many%20volunteers%20were%20provided%20comprehensive%20training%20to%20tackle%20forest%20fires.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20Pritam%2C%20THF%E2%80%99s%20initiative%20of%20preventing%20forest%20fire%20has%20seen%205%2C066%20young%20firefighters%20being%20trained%20in%201%2C000%20villages%20under%2010%20development%20blocks%20of%20Pauri%20Garhwal%2C%20Tehri%20Garhwal%2C%20Almora%2C%20and%20Bageshwar%20districts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20THF%20has%20also%20enhanced%20community%20resilience%20by%20reviving%20the%20%E2%80%98Van%20Panchayat%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20a%20local%20community%20group%20responsible%20for%20forest%20management%2C%20as%20well%20as%20encouraging%20the%20plantation%20of%20fire-resistant%20species%2C%20and%20raising%20awareness%20through%20%3Cem%3ENukkad%20Natak%20%3C%2Fem%3E(street%20play)%2C%20rallies%2C%20wall%20writing%2C%20quiz%20competition%2C%20radio%20programs%2C%20and%20jingles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20the%20region%20has%20observed%20a%20significant%20decrease%20of%20about%2053.33%20percent%20%E2%80%94%20from%2030%20forest%20fire%20incidents%20in%202019-21%20to%2014%20in%202022.%20Similarly%2C%20a%2057.35%20percent%20reduction%20was%20observed%20in%20the%20area%20affected%20by%20forest%20fires%20%E2%80%94%20from%2037.05%20to%2015.8%20hectares%20in%20the%20same%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEncouraged%20by%20the%20results%20of%20the%20community-driven%20approach%2C%20Pritam%20requests%20local%20people%20in%20the%20fire-prone%20regions%20to%20step%20up%20and%20respond%20to%20emergencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20%3Cem%3Ejal%20%3C%2Fem%3E(water)%2C%20%3Cem%3Ejungle%20%3C%2Fem%3E(forest)%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Ejameen%20%3C%2Fem%3E(land)%20belong%20to%20all%20of%20us%20as%20a%20community%2C%20so%20it%20is%20our%20responsibility%20to%20step%20up%20to%20safeguard%20it.%20We%20need%20to%20take%20more%20responsibility%20and%20consciously%20increase%20our%20awareness%20against%20forest%20fires.%20In%20the%20past%20couple%20of%20years%2C%20we%20have%20been%20able%20to%20bust%20myths%20among%20villagers%20and%20reduce%20extreme%20forest%20fire%20incidences%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Pritam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20we%20could%20do%20it%2C%20then%20you%20too%20can.%20This%20Forest%20Day%2C%20let%E2%80%99s%20pledge%20to%20save%20our%20jungles!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20photos%20courtesy%20The%20Hans%20Foundation)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fdehradun%2Fukhand-loses-highest-561-2-ha-green-cover-in-24hrs-to-fires-over-2k-ha-so-far%2Farticleshow%2F91136591.cms%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%2