0gaining%20traction%20at%20the%20time.%20We%20first%20launched%20the%20Holi%20colours%20in%202018%20and%20have%20been%20receiving%20more%20orders%20ever%20since%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gaurang%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20the%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F313885%2Fhyderabad-manya-cherabuddi-makes-natural-dyes-conducts-workshops-sustainable-living%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20colour-making%20process%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20Gaurang%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20colours%20are%20entirely%20natural%20and%20made%20from%20edible%20materials.%20The%20base%20is%20maize%20flour%20cultivated%20by%20the%20community%20itself.%20The%20orange%20colour%20is%20derived%20from%20the%20Palash%20flower%2C%20abundant%20in%20the%20area%20during%20March%20and%20April.%20Our%20yellow%20hue%20combines%20Palash%20flowers%20with%20a%20touch%20of%20turmeric.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGreen%20hues%20are%20concocted%20from%20a%20blend%20of%20various%20forest%20leaves.%20%E2%80%9CLastly%2C%20we%20have%20a%20pink%20shade%20crafted%20using%20Ganganagri%20Rose%20along%20with%20a%20hint%20of%20dried%20beetroot%2C%20which%20enhances%20the%20vibrancy%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20flowers%20are%20first%20picked%2C%20sorted%20and%20cleaned.%20The%20ingredients%20are%20boiled%20for%2014-15%20minutes%20and%20then%20they%20are%20sieved%20to%20segregate%20the%20residue.%20Once%20this%20is%20done%2C%20the%20mixture%20is%20dried%20and%20then%20hand-pounded.%20This%20is%20then%20added%20to%20the%20organic%20maize%20flour%20to%20make%20natural%20colours.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20primarily%20serves%20customers%20in%20Maharashtra%20with%20a%20few%20others%20from%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20country%2C%20along%20with%20numerous%20wholesale%20partners%20who%20sell%20these%20products%20as%20well.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20retail%20through%20our%20website%20and%20Amazon%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gaurang%20mentions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fbhil-2-1710941720.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20tribals%20handmade%20all%20the%20colours%20using%20flowers%20like%20Palash%20and%20Ganaganagri%20Rose.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fbhil-2-1710941720.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fbhil-2-1710941720-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fbhil-2-1710941720-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fbhil-2-1710941720-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fbhil-2-1710941720-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345349%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20tribals%20handmade%20all%20the%20colours%20using%20flowers%20like%20Palash%20and%20Ganaganagri%20Rose.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20the%20company%20has%20already%20sold%20over%20four%20tonnes%20of%20colours!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJatin%20Desai%2C%20a%20repeat%20customer%2C%20attests%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20my%20second%20year%20purchasing%20the%20product.%20The%20colours%20are%20skin-friendly%20and%20breathable%2C%20leaving%20no%20long-lasting%20skin%20discolouration.%20They%20can%20be%20easily%20washed%20off%20on%20the%20same%20day%2C%20with%20only%20minimal%20residual%20tint.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20company%E2%80%99s%20consumer%20base%20continues%20to%20expand%2C%20Gaurang%20emphasises%20that%20the%20community%20remains%20their%20top%20priority.%20%E2%80%9COur%20primary%20objective%20has%20always%20been%20to%20prioritise%20the%20community%20and%20their%20needs.%20This%20art%20has%20been%20a%20part%20of%20our%20country%20for%20generations%2C%20and%20it%20must%20be%20preserved.%20Why%20resort%20to%20chemical%20and%20synthetic%20alternatives%20when%20we%20have%20perfectly%20natural%20and%20traditional%20products%20available%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20asserts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EYou%20can%20buy%20your%20packs%20of%20organic%20colour%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.monksbouffe.com%2Fproducts%2Fabeer-herbal-holi-colours-bhil-tribals%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3B%20All%20Pictures%20Credit%3A%20Monks%20Bouffe)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710944782000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fbhil-1710941440.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D345330%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Brothers%20Gaurang%20and%20Saurabh%20Motta%20launched%20'Abeer%E2%80%99%20with%20the%20aim%20to%20save%20Bhil%20tribe%E2%80%99s%20dying%20art%20of%20making%20natural%20Holi%20colours%20using%20flowers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A22%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F345330%2Fabeer-natural-holi-colours-made-of-flowers-by-mumbai-brothers-gaurang-saurabh-motta-bhil-tribe%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Always%20Crave%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20Momos%E2%80%99%3A%20Indian%20Women%20Run%20Momo%20Truck%20While%20Juggling%20Full-Time%20Jobs%20in%20the%20US%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOn%20any%20given%20day%20the%20streets%20of%20New%20Jersey%20are%20bustling%20%E2%80%94%20office%20goers%20rushing%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20skip%20the%20traffic%20jam%2C%20the%20consistent%20hum%20drum%20of%20buses%2C%20the%20chatter%20of%20school%20kids%2C%20regular%20joggers%20trying