n%20and%20FAQs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20initial%20idea%20behind%20starting%20this%20platform%20was%20to%20educate%20people.%20Exposure%20to%20knowledge%20and%20access%20to%20basic%20legalities%20is%20sorely%20missing%20here.%20We%20provide%20you%20with%20all%20the%20information%20that%20you%20need%20even%20before%20visiting%20a%20lawyer.%20You%20want%20to%20file%20an%20FIR%3F%20Here%E2%80%99s%20a%20template%20which%20you%20just%20need%20to%20fill%20in%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20the%20young%20lawyer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20the%20different%20packages%20that%20Rest%20the%20Case%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F295748%2Fkochi-law-student-breaks-stereotypes-about-women-bus-drivers-ann-mary%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprovides%20to%20lawyers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20they%20allow%20them%20to%20help%20with%20leads%20and%20display%20their%20profile.%20They%20also%20provide%20a%20Client%20Management%20System%20(CMS)%20to%20help%20the%20lawyers%20manage%20and%20document%20the%20data.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESiddhant%20Deshpande%2C%20a%20criminal%20lawyer%20practising%20at%20the%20Bombay%20High%20Court%2C%20states%20that%20Rest%20The%20Case%20has%20helped%20him%20with%20over%2010%20leads%20so%20far%2C%20which%20is%20helpful%20for%20young%20lawyers%20to%20gain%20a%20good%20customer%20base%20and%20handle%20a%20variety%20of%20cases.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20found%20the%20company%20through%20social%20media.%20What%20is%20unique%20about%20them%20is%20the%20fact%20that%20they%20give%20you%20verified%20leads%20(clients)%20and%20help%20you%20with%20all%20the%20background%20information.%20They%20give%20you%20a%20pretty%20good%20deal%20and%20think%20about%20the%20welfare%20of%20both%20the%20clients%20and%20the%20lawyers%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Siddhant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESo%2C%20how%20are%20the%20lawyers%20vetted%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEa